quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaf: Ka Qura‘n e tlotlehang (u morumuoa oa Allah)"
  50,2,"Empa ba maketse hore na ho tlile morumuoa ho bona ea hlahang har’a bona. Kahoo mahana-tumelo ba re: “ena ke ntho e makatsang"
  50,3,"Eng! Mohlang re shoang, re fetohile lerole, re ka boela ra tsosoa hape? Seo ke poelo e thoko haholo.”"
  50,4,"Re tseba tseo lefats’e le li jereng tsa bona, Re na le Lenane la litlaleho"
  50,5,Empa ba nyelisa ‘nete nakong eo e tlang ho bona; kahoo ba pherekanong
  50,6,Na ha ba shebeng marung holim’a bona? – Kamoo Re a entseng kateng le kamoo Re’a khabisitseng kateng; le kamoo ho senang sekoli kateng
  50,7,"Le lefats’e Re le alile le hona ho tsepamisa lithaba holim’a lona, eaba Re etsa hore limela tsohle tse khahlehang li mele holim’a lona, –"
  50,8,"E le pontso le sona sehopotso molemong oa lekhabunyane lefe, kapa lefe le sokolohileng"
  50,9,Re romella pula e hlohonolofetseng lefats’eng eo ka eona re phelisang lijalo lirapeng le tsona lijo thollo
  50,10,Le lifate tsa lipalema tse jereng liririella tsa litholoana; –
  50,11,Ele phepo molemong oa batho; e bile Re phelisa lefats’e le omeletseng ka pula. Ka mokhoa oo Tsoho Ea Bafu e tla bang kateng
  50,12,"Batho ba habo Nooe ba ile ba nyefola ‘nete pele ho bona, ka mokhoa o ts’oanang le baahi ba Rass, Ba – Thamude"
  50,13,"Ba – a’ad, Faro, le bana ba bo Lota"
  50,14,"Le baahi ba Mediane, le batho ba Tubb’a: morabe o mong le o mong o ile oa nyefola baromuoa; Tlhokomeliso ea Ka e ile ea phethahatsoa(holim’a bona)"
  50,15,Na Re ile Ra tepella ke tlholeho ea mathomo? Hore ebe ba na le khoao ka tlholeho e ncha
  50,16,"Ke Rona ba hlotseng motho, Re tseba ka botlalo seo moea oa hae o mo hlohleletsang sona, etsoe Re haufi haholo le eena ho feta mahalapa a hae"
  50,17,"Hopola manyeloi a mabeli a khethiloe ho ngola liketso tsa motho, le leng le lutse ka letsohong le letona, ha le leng lona le lutse ka letsohong le lets’ehali"
  50,18,Ha ho lentsoe leha le le leng leo a le buoang e be moalosi oa hae ha a le ngole
  50,19,"Mahlomola a lefu a tlisa ‘nete(kapel’a mahlo a hae): “Sena ke sona seo u neng u leka ho se qoba.”"
  50,20,"Terompeta e tla letsoa: Lena ke letsatsi le ts’episitsoeng"
  50,21,Moea ka mong o tla atamela le lenyeloi le o qhobang esitana le la paki
  50,22,"(Ho tla thoe;) “Ha u e’a ka oa tsotella molaetsa ona. Hajoale Re phetlile sekhurumetso sa lona, mahlo a lona a ncho-cho kajeno.”"
  50,23,"Moalosi oa hae o tla re: “tlaleho ea hae ke na le eona.”"
  50,24,"(Kahlolo e tla ba:) “akhelang mong le mong eo e leng molatoli oa Allah kahar’a lihele! –"
  50,25,"Ea neng a sitisa toka, a tlola meeli eohle, a jala khoao le lipelaelo,”"
  50,26,“Le hona ho iketsetsa molingoana kantle ho Allah. Mo akheleng kahar’a kahlolo e ts’abehang.”
  50,27,"Motsoalle oa hae o tla re: “Mong`a ka! Ha se ‘na ea mo rutileng ho tlola meeli, empa o ne a khelohetse thoko.”"
  50,28,"Allah U tla re: “Se pheheng khang kapel’a Ka, khale Ke le romeletse tlhokomeliso"
  50,29,"“Molaetsa o tsoang ho ‘Na o ke ke oa fetoha, ha ho kamoo Nka hlokelang makhabunyane toka kateng.”"
  50,30,"Ka letsatsi le leng Re botsa lihele: “Na o tletse haholo?” Li tla re: “Na ho sa le teng ba bang ba tlang?”"
  50,31,"Serapa se tla atametsoa haufinyane le bohle ba etsang botle, se ke ke sa eba thoko le bona"
  50,32,"(Lentsoe le tla re:) “sena ke seo le neng le se ts’episitsoe, – ho bohle ba sokolohileng esita le hona ho ho boloka (Molao oa Hae)"
  50,33,"“Ba ts’abileng(Allah) Ea Tletseng Lereko sephiring, le ho tla ka pelo e sokolohileng"
  50,34,“Kenang kahar’a sona ka Khotso le Polokeho; Lena ke Letsatsi la Bophelo bo sa feleng.”
  50,35,"Ba tla fumana tsohle tseo ba li labalabelang kamoo, – ho teng lintho tse ngata ho Rona"
  50,36,"Hana ke meloko e mekae eo Re ileng Ra e ripitla pele ho bona, eo e neng e le linatla ho ba feta ka matla hooba neng ba tletse- tletse le lefats’e! Na ba ne ba ena le sebaka sa ho phonyoha nakong eo kahlolo eba oelang"
  50,37,Ruri
  50,38,Re hlotse maholimo le lefats’e le tsohle tse teng lipakeng tsa ona ka matsatsi a ts’eletseng kantle le mokhathala o kileng oa Re ama
  50,39,"Eba le mamello ho tsohle tseo ba li buoang, u keteke lithoriso tsa Mong`a hau pele letsatsi le chaba le pele le likela"
  50,40,"Le karolong ea bosiu, keteka lithoriso tsa Hae, le kamor’a lithapelo"
  50,41,"U mamele mohla letsatsi leo ka lona seboholi se tlang ho hoelehetsa se le sebakeng se haufinyane, –"
  50,42,"Mohlang ba tlang ho utloa molumo o ts’abehang ka ‘nete: Leo e tla ba Letsatsi la Tsoho"
  50,43,"Ruri! Ke Rona ba fanang ka Bophelo le Lefu, poelo ea lona bohle e ho Rona"
  50,44,"Letsatsi leo ka lona lefats’e le tlang ho peperana, ba tla tlaba phasa-phasa ka hohle. Ke ka mokhoa o bobebe oo Re tlang ho ba khobokanya ka ona"
  50,45,Re tseba ka botlalo seo ba se buang; ha se uena ea tlamehang ho ba qobella. Kahoo ba lemose ka Qura’n bohle ba ts’abang Kahlolo ea Ka
  51,1,Ka liphefo tse jalang
  51,2,Le tse phahamisang le ho jara mojaro o boima
  51,3,Le tse fokang ka monyebe
  51,4,Le tse phatlalatsang mahloholono tlas’a taelo
  51,5,Ruri! Tseo le li ts’episitsoeng ke ‘nete
  51,6,Ruri Kahlolo le Toka li tla phethahala
  51,7,Ka leholimo le Litsela tse ngata
  51,8,"Ruri, puo tsa lona li fapane"
  51,9,Tseo ka tsona le khelosang (hole le `nete) ba tlang ho kheloha
  51,10,Sekhobo se be ho bo raleshano
  51,11,Ba loebaloebang kahar’a sekh’ola sa pherekano
  51,12,"Ba a botsa, “Letsatsi la kahlolo le Toka le tla ba neng?”"
  51,13,(E tla ba) Letsatsi leo ka lona ba tlang ho ahloloa kahar’a Mollo
  51,14,“Latsoang kahlolo eo le ipitselitseng eona. Sena ke sona seo le neng le ba tla ho se potlakisa.”
  51,15,"Haele ba lokileng, ba tla phela kahar’a Lirapa le Liliba tse kopotsang"
  51,16,"Ba thabisoe ke lintho tsohle tseo Mong`a bona A ba fang tsona; hobane, pele ho moo, ba ne ba phela bophelo bo hloekileng"
  51,17,Ba ne ba tloaetse ho robala hanyenyane feela bosiu
  51,18,Le lihoreng tsa meso ba rapella ts’oarelo
  51,19,"Mekopa-kopa le mafutsana a ne a e na le seabo thepeng ea bona, ea kopang, le ea thibetsoeng ho kopa"
  51,20,Lefats’eng ho teng Lits’upiso ho bohle ba nang le Tumelo ea sebele
  51,21,"Le ho lona lits’upiso li teng: Na ha le bone"
  51,22,Leholimong teng ke naleng ea lona le linthong tsohle tseo le li ts’episitsoeng
  51,23,"Ka Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e, sena ke ‘nete, joaloka ha e le ‘nete, hore le tseba ho buisana"
  51,24,Na pale ea Abrahama le baeti ba hae ba neng ba hlompheha e kile ea fihla ho uena
  51,25,"Mohla ba neng ba fihla ho eena ba re: “Khotso!” Eaba o’a araba, “Khotso!”: “Ba shebahala ba sa tloaeleha.”"
  51,26,"A boela kapele ho ba lelapa la hae, eaba o tlisa namane e halikiloeng"
  51,27,"A e beha kapel’a bona, a re: “Na le tla ja?”"
  51,28,"A simolla hoba ts’aba. Eaba ba re: “Se ts’abe letho!” Ba mo neha litaba tse molemo tsa tlhaho ea mora ea sitsitsoeng ka tsebo"
  51,29,"Empa mosali oa hae a atamela ka lentsoe le phahameng, a ikotla sefahleho a re: “Mosali ea tsofetseng oa nyopa!”"
  51,30,"Baeti ba re: “Leha ho le joalo, ho rialo Mong`a hau. Ruri! Ke Eena Ea Seli, Ea Tsebang.”"
  51,31,"(Abrahama) a re: “Ke eng seo le tlileng ka sona lona Baromuoa ba Allah?”"
  51,32,Ba re“Re romeletsoe ho batho ba qoetseng sebeng; –
  51,33,“Ho tla ba romella lehlohlojane la lenyeta
  51,34,“E le sesupo se tsoang ho Mong`a hau ho ba tlolang meeli.”
  51,35,Ra pholosa ba-kholoang ba neng ba le teng moo
  51,36,Empa Re ile Ra fumana lelapa le le leng feela la ba inehetseng ho Allah
  51,37,Eaba Re ba siea le sesupo molemong oaba ts’abang Kahlolo e Mahlonoko
  51,38,"Le ho Moshe ho teng sesupo, Re ile Ra mo romella ho Faro ka bopaki bo totobetseng"
  51,39,"Empa Faro o ile a furalla le Matona a hae, a re: “Moloi, kapa lehlanya.”"
  51,40,"Kahoo, Re ile Ra mo nka hammoho le lebotho la hae, eaba Re ba khamisa leoatle, hobane o ne a fosahetse"
  51,41,"Le ho morabe oa Ba–A’d ho teng sesupo, Re ile Ra romella leholi’atsana kahlanong le bona"
  51,42,"Le sa kang la siea letho moo le fetileng teng, lintho tsohle li ile tsa fetoha lesupi"
  51,43,"Le ho Ba-Thamud ho teng sesupo, Bonang ba ile ba bolelloa, “Natefeloang ha nakoana!”"
  51,44,"Empa ba ile ba eba khahlanong le molao oa Mong`a bona ka tello: eaba ba nanoloa ke ho reketla ho lumang ba sa ntse ba shebile"
  51,45,Hoo ba sitiloeng le ho ema (ka maoto) kapa ho ithusa ka bo- bona
  51,46,"Joaloka batho ba habo Nooe pele ho bona: Hobane ba ile ba tlola meeli hampe"
  51,47,"Re ahile Leholimo ka Matla le Tsebo, Hobane ke Rona ba hlotseng bophara ba leholimo"
  51,48,"Ebile Re alile lefats’e: Re le ala ka makhethe ha kakang"
  51,49,"Re hlotse lintho tsohle ka bobeli, hore le tle le amohele taelo"
  51,50,"Potlakelang ho Allah ke hona: Ke molemosi ea hlakileng ho lona ea tsoang ho Allah"
  51,51,"Le se iketsetse molingoana ofe, kapa ofe papisong le Allah: Ke molemosi ea hlakileng ho lona ea tsoang ho Eena"
  51,52,"Joaloka ha ho se moromuoa ofe, kapa ofe ea kileng a tla ho Batho pele ho bona e be ha ba re: “Ke moloi, kapa lehlanya!”"
  51,53,"Na ke moetlo oo ba o neheletsaneng? Che, ke batho ba tlolang meeli eohle"
  51,54,"Ba furalle: uena ha u na molato"
  51,55,"Empa ruta (Molaetsa oa hae): hobane thuto e molemo ho Ba- kholoang"
  51,56,Ke hlotse tse sa bonoeng (li-jinn) le batho molemong oa hore ba Nts’ebeletse
  51,57,"Ha ho leo ke le kopang ho bona: kapa ho hloka phepo ho bona"
  51,58,"Hobane Ke Allah Ea fanang ka bophelo, Mong`a Ts’episo, Ea sa Thekeseleng"
  51,59,"Hobane beatsalibe karolo ea bona e ts’oana le karolo ea mehahabo bona (ea meloko ea pele): kahoo, ba se Nkope ho potlakissa (karolo eo)"
  51,60,"Sekhobo se be holim’a mahana-tumelo, boikarabellong ba Letsatsi la bona leo ba le ts’episitsoeng"
  52,1,Ka leralla (le Ts’enolo)
  52,2,Ka Molao o Ngoliloeng
  52,3,Holim’a letlalo le manolotsoeng
  52,4,Ka ntlo e chakeloang mehla eohle
  52,5,Ka Sekhele Se Phahamiselitsoeng Holimo-limo
  52,6,Le ka Leoatle le tletseng
  52,7,Ruri! Kahlolo ea Mong`a hau e tla phethahatsoa
  52,8,"Ha ho mang, kapa mang ea ka e thibelang"
  52,9,Letsatsi leo ka lona leholimo le tlang ho sisinyeha ha mpe
  52,10,Lithaba li tlang ho fofela mona le mane
  52,11,Sekhobo letsatsing leo se be holim’a bohle ba nkang ‘nete e le leshano
  52,12,Ba har’a bosaoana ba leshano
  52,13,"Letsatsi leo ba tla sutuletsoa ka har’a lihele, ho se khanyetso"
  52,14,"“Ona”, ho tla thoe: “Ke mollo, – oo le neng le tloaetse ho o hana"
  52,15,"“Na ke mafeela, kapa ebe ha le bone"
  52,16,"“Chesoang ka teng, ho ea ts’oana hore le ea o mamella kapa che: le mpa le amohela moputso oa liketso tsa lona.”"
  52,17,"Ruri! ba topileng ts’ebeletsong ea bona, ba tla phela kahar’a Lirapa le nyakallo"
  52,18,"Ba thabisitsoe ke tseo Mong`a bona aba sitsitseng ka tsona, Mong`a bona U tla ba lopolla Kotlong ea Mollo"
  52,19,"(Ho tla thoe ho bona:) “le je le noe, ka phaello le bophelo ka lebaka la liketso tsa lona.”"
  52,20,Ba tla phomola holim’a Literone tse hlophisitsoeng ka mekhahlelo. Re tla ba nyalisa basali ba mahlo a nchocho a khahlang
  52,21,"Bohle Ba-Kholoang, ba bile ba setsoe morao ke malapa a bona Tumelong, Re tla ba matahants’a le malapa a bona, ha Re ke ke Ra fokotsa meputso ea liketso tsa bona. Motho e mong le e mong ke paki liketsong tsa hae"
  52,22,"Re tla ba sitsa ka litholoana le nama, tsohle tseo ba li thabelang"
  52,23,"Kamoo, ba tla neheletsana senoelo se hloekileng malebana le ts’ila efe, se senang koli"
  52,24,"Ho tla ba le basebeletsi ba ntseng ba tsamaea har’a bona ba ts’oanang le bona, ba joaloka likhetla tse neng li patiloe"
  52,25,"Ba tla atamelana, ba botsana"
  52,26,"Ba tla re: “Pele-pele re ne re se na ts’abo, sebakeng sa mehahabo rona"
  52,27,"“Empa Allah U bile lereko ho rona, A ba A re lopolla kahlolong ea Moea o Chesang"
  52,28,"“Ruri! Re ile ra bitsa ho Eena khale. Ruri! Ke Eena ‘Maballi, Ea Tletseng Mohau.”"
  52,29,"Phatlalatsa ke hona Lithoriso (tsa Mong’a hau). Hobane ka Lereko la Mong’a hau, ha u senohe, kapa lona lehlanya"
  52,30,"Kapa ebe ba re: “Ke sereneketsi, seo re lebeletseng mats’oenyeho tlas’a nako holim’a hae!”"
  52,31,"Uena e re: “Letang! Le ‘na ke tla leta le lona.”"
  52,32,"Na ebe ke likelello tsa bona tse ba susumetsang ho etsa tje, kapa empa e le batho ba tlolang meeli"
  52,33,"Kapa ba re: “O iqapetse (Molaetsa)?” Che ha ba na Tumelo"
  52,34,Ha ba hlahise ts’enolo e ts’oanang le ena haeba ba buoa ‘Nete
  52,35,Kapa ebe ba hlotsoe ke letho? Kapa e be ke bona ba hlolang
  52,36,"Kapa ba hlotse maholimo le lefats’e? Che, ha ban a tumelo e tiileng"
  52,37,"Kapa matlotlo a Mong`a hau a ho bona, Kapa ba filoe boikarabello holim’a ona"
  52,38,"Kapa ba na le tsela e ka fihlang leholimong, ba mamela makunutu a lona. Momameli har’a bona ha a ke a hlahise bopaki bo hlakileng"
  52,39,Kapa ebe Allah U na le barali ha lona le ena le bara
  52,40,"kapa ebe u ba kopa moputso, hore ba jare mokoloto"
  52,41,"Kapa tse sa bonoeng li matsohong a bona, ba li ngola fats’e"
  52,42,"Kapa ba u lohela leraba? Empa ba nyefoli ba Allah, ke bona ba pitliloeng"
  52,43,Kapa ba na le molimo e mong ntle ho Allah? Tlotla ebe ho Allah Ea phahametseng tsohle tseo ba li bapisang le Eena
  52,44,"Hoja ba ne ba ka bona leqhetsoana la leholimo le oela fats’e, ba ne ba tla re: “Ke pokella ea maru.”"
  52,45,"Kahoo ba lese, ho fihlela ba thulana le Letsatsi la bona leo ka lona ba tlang ho ilibana (ke letsoalo)"
  52,46,"Letsatsing leo maraba a bona a ke ke a thusa ka letho, ba ke ke ba fumana thuso"
  52,47,"Ruri bohle baetsalibe, kahlolo e teng kathoko ho ena. Empa bongataa bona ha bo utloisisi"
  52,48,"Joale leta ka mamello taelo ea Mong`a hau: hobane uena u kapel’a mahlo a Rona; u keteke lithoriso tsa Mong`a hau nakong eo u emeng thapelong"
  52,49,"Le karolong ea bosiu u rorise Mong`a hau, – le ha linaleli li il’o likela"
  53,1,Ka naleli ha e ea malikelong
  53,2,"Motsoalle oa lona ha a ea kheloha, kapa hona ho thetsoa"
  53,3,Leha ele hona ho buoa litakatso tsa hae
  53,4,Haese ts’usumetso e romeletsoeng ho eena
  53,5,O e rutiloe ke Ea Matla a Ts’abehang
  53,6,"Ea Seli: hobane u hlaheletse ka mahetla"
  53,7,"A sa le sebakanyana, hojana mane"
  53,8,A atamela; a ba haufinyane
  53,9,"Ho fihlela a le sebaka sa bolelele ba liqha tse peli ho tloha ho eena, kapa haufi ho feta moo"
  53,10,Eaba Allah U senolela lekhabunyane la Hae sohle seo A ileng A mo senolela sona
  53,11,"Joale, ke pelo e ke keng ea thetsa ho latela seo e se boneng"
  53,12,Na joale le tla mo phehisa khang ka seo a se boneng
  53,13,O ile a mo bona lekhetlo la bobeli a theoha
  53,14,A le haufi le sefate sa Leoka seo ho ke keng hoa feta ope
  53,15,Seo haufi le sona eleng Serapa sa Lehae
  53,16,Bonang! Sefate sa Leoka patehile
  53,17,"Mahlo a hae a ne a sa chalike, kapa ho etsa phoso"
  53,18,"Ruri! U ile a bona e ngoe Lits’enolo tsa Mong`a hae, e kholohali"
  53,19,"Le kile la bona Lat, le Uzza"
  53,20,"Le Manat e mong oa boraro, (melingoana)"
  53,21,"Eng! Lona le ikhethela botona, empa Allah Eena le mo khethela bots’ehali"
  53,22,Seo e ne e tla ba karohano e se nang toka
  53,23,"Empa e le mabitso ao le iqapetseng, – lona le bo-ntata lona, – ha ho bopaki boo Allah a kileng a bo romela. Ba latela likhakanyo le litabatabelo tsa meea ea bona! – Le ha tataiso e tsoang ho Mong`a bona ese e finyeletse ho bona"
  53,24,"Che, na motho o tla fumana sohle seo a se lakatsang"
  53,25,Empa ke Allah eo Qetello le Qalo ea tsohle e leng tsa Hae
  53,26,Hore na ke manyeloi a makae a maholimong puello ea ona e sa tlong ho thusa letho kantle hore feela Allah A fane ka tumello ho eo A khahlaong ke eena le hona ho mo khetha
  53,27,"Haele ba sa kholoeng Bophelong Bo-tlang, ba rehang manyeloi mabitso a basali"
  53,28,"Empa ha ba na tsebo ka seo. Ba mpa ba latela likhakanyo, Likhakanyo li ke keng tsa nka sebaka sa ‘nete"
  53,29,"Kahoo sutha pel’a bohle ba furallang molaetsa oa Rona, ba ithatela bophelo ba lefats’e lena"
  53,30,"Tsebo ea bona e fella hona moo. Ruri! Mong`a hau o hlokolosi kaba khelohileng tseleng ea Hae, e bile o hlokolosi ka ho fetisisa ka bohle ba amohelang tataiso"
  53,31,"Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng ke tsa Allah: hore A tle A putse bohle ba etsang sebe ka tseo ba li entseng esita le hona ho putsa bohle ba etsang toka ka tse lokileng"
  53,32,"Haele bohle ba qobang libe tse kholo le liketso tse hlabisang lihlong, kantle le liphoso tse fokolang –Ruri! ts’oarelo ea Mong`a hau e senyekhenyekhe. U hlokolosi ka lona ho tloha ts’imolohong ea lona lefats’eng le nakong eo le neng le patehile lipopelong tsa bo-’ma lona. Kahoo, le se ikuke le hloekile bo- lona. Ke Eena ea hlokolosi ka ho fetisisa khahlanong le bobe"
  53,33,Na u lemoha ea koenehang
  53,34,A fana hanyenyane le hona ho tiisa pelo
  53,35,Eng! Na o na le tsebo ka Liphiri hoo a li bonang
  53,36,"Che, ha a na tsebo ka litaba tse ka har’a mangolo a Moshe –"
  53,37,"Le Abrahama ea ileng a phethahatsa litaelo: –"
  53,38,Tsa hore ha ho motho ea ka jarang mojaro oa motho e mong
  53,39,"Hore ha ho motho ofe, kapa ofe ea tla amohela seo a sa se sebeletsang"
  53,40,Hore ts’ebetso ea hae e tla hlahela pooaneng
  53,41,"Joale, o tla lefshoa ho latela ts’ebetso eo ka tefo e feletseng"
  53,42,Hore ho Mong`a hau ke katlehong ea qetelo
  53,43,Hore ke Eena ea faneng ka Nyakallo le Lillo
  53,44,Hore ke Eena ea fanang ka Lefu le Bophelo
  53,45,"Hore ke Eena ea hlotseng lintho ka bobeli, – tse tona le tse ts’ehali"
  53,46,Ho tsoa lerotholing le tsoileng
  53,47,Hore ke Eena ea ts’episitseng Tsoho bophelong bo-tlang
  53,48,Hore ke Eena ea fanang ka Borui le Khotsofalo
  53,49,Hore ke Eena Mong`a Sirius (Naleli e Kholo)
  53,50,Le hore ke Eena ea ripitlileng morabe oa mathomo oa Ba – A’d
  53,51,"Le Ba-Thamude, ha ho ope ea ileng a phonyoha"
  53,52,"Le batho ba habo Nooe pele ho bona, hobane e ne e le bahanyapetsi, batloli ba meeli"
  53,53,U bile A ripitla le Metse (Ea Sodoma le Gomorah)
  53,54,Hore e koaelehe
  53,55,"Joale, ke mahlohonolo afe a Mong`a hau ao uena motho o ka a phehisang khang"
  53,56,Enoa ke molemosi oa ba lemosi ba ileng ba tla khale-khale
  53,57,Kahlolo e ea e ntse e atamela haufi
  53,58,"Ha ho mang, haese Allah feela Ea ka e utullang"
  53,59,Na le makalitsoe ke boemo boo ba litaba
  53,60,"Ebile le ea nyakalla, le fapana le ho lla, –"
  53,61,Le qhala nako ea lona ka mafeela
  53,62,Empa le ithapalatsa kapel’a Allah le Mo sebeletse ka lerato
  54,1,"Hora (Ea Kahlolo) e se e atametse, ngoeli petsohile ka lehare"
  54,2,"Empa ha ba bona sesupo, ba ea koeneha, ba re: “Hona ke boloi ba ka mehla.”"
  54,3,"Ba nyelisa ‘nete, ba sala litakatso tsa bona morao. Empa, ntho e ngoe le e ngoe e na le nako ea pallo"
  54,4,"Ba amohetse litaba tsa temoso e feletseng, hore ba fetole metsamao ea bona"
  54,5,Bohlale bo tsotoang; empa litemoso ha li’a ka tsa thusa letho
  54,6,Kahoo ba furalle. Letsatsi leo ka lona sebohloli se tlang ho ba bitsetsa litabeng tse mahlonoko
  54,7,"Ba tla atamela, – ba soabile – mabitleng a bona, ba ts’oana le litsie ha li tletse-tletse hohle"
  54,8,Ba potlaketse ho seboholi ba tonne mahlo! – “Le thata Letsatsi.” Mahana-tumelo a tla cho
  54,9,"Batho ba habo Nooe pele ho bona ba ile ba nyefola lekhabunyane la Rona pele ho bona, ba re: “Ke lehlanya!” O ile a phalalisoa"
  54,10,"Ke moo a ileng a bitsa ho Mong`a hae: “Ke ea hlotsoeng, kahoo ak’u mpe U nthuse.”"
  54,11,Eaba Re bula mekoallo ea leholimo ka metsi a phallang
  54,12,"Le hona ho ts’akhunya liliba lefats’eng, hore metsi a tle a fihlele taelo e fanoeng"
  54,13,Eaba Re mo jara ka Areka eneng e entsoe ka lifate tsa lipalema
  54,14,"Hore e phaphamale holim’a metsi kapel’a mahlo a Rona, e le moputso ho eo ea ileng a nyelisoa"
  54,15,Re ile Ra siea seo e le sesupo; empa na ho teng ea tlang ho amohela temoso
  54,16,Empa ak’u boneng kamoo kahlolo ea ka e ileng ea ts’abeha kateng kamor’a litemoso tsa ka
  54,17,Ka ‘nete Re entse Qura’n ho ba bobebe ho ho utloisiseha le ho hopoleha; joale na ho teng ea tla amohela temoso
  54,18,Morabe oa Ba-A’d o ile oa nyelisa. Bonang kamoo kahlolo ea Ka e ileng ea ts’abeha kateng kamor’a litemoso
  54,19,Hobane Re ile Ra ba romella sekhobo sa phefo mohla letsatsi le nyonyehang
  54,20,Hoo e ileng ea tsokotsa batho joaloka ha eka ene ele likutu tse koqotsoeng ka metso tsa lifate tsa palema
  54,21,Bonang kamoo kahlolo ea Ka e ileng ea ts’abeha kateng kamor’a litemoso tsa Ka
  54,22,Ruri! Re entse koran ho ba bobebe ho utloisiseha le ho hopoleha; joale na ho teng ea tlang ho amohela temoso
  54,23,Ba-Thamude ba ile ba nyelisa Balemosi
  54,24,"Hobane ba ile ba re: “Eng! Monna a le mong feela har’a rona, re ka mo latela? Ruri! Re tla be re lahlehetsoe ke menahano, re hlanya"
  54,25,"“Na molaetsa o filoe eena Salih feela har’a rona? Che, empa e le moqabanyi ea leshano.”"
  54,26,Hosane ba tla tseba hore na ke mang ea leshano
  54,27,"Hobane Re tla romella kamele e ts’ehali ele teko khahlano le bona, kahoo u ba lebelle, u be le mamello"
  54,28,"U ba tsebise hore ba arolelana metsi le eona, ba lokela ho noa ka tlhatlhamano"
  54,29,"Empa ba ileba bitsa e mong oa bona, eaba o nka sabole; a e bolaea"
  54,30,Bonang kamoo kahlolo ea Ka e ileng ea ts’abeha kateng kamor’a hore Ke fane ka litemoso
  54,31,"Hobane Re ile Ra ba romella molumo o matla o le mong feela, eaba ba fetoha lesupi"
  54,32,Ruri Re entse Qura’n ho ba bobebe ho utloisiseha le ho hopoleha; joale na o teng ea tla amohela temoso
  54,33,"Batho ba habo Lota, ba ‘nile ba nyefola Temoso"
  54,34,"Re ile Ra romella sefako sa majoe holim’a bona kaofela kantle ho lelapa la lota, eo Re ileng Ra mo pholosa esale ka matjeke"
  54,35,Ele Lereko ho tsoa ho Rona. Ke kamoo Re putsang ba fanang ka liteboho
  54,36,"O (Lota) ‘nile a ba lemosa ka kotlo ea Rona, empa ba ile ba hanyetsa Temoso"
  54,37,"Ba bile ba mo tsekisa baeti ba hae, empa Ra ba foufatsa.(ba utloa) “Latsoang kahlolo ea Ka kamor’a Temoso ea Ka.”"
  54,38,Kahlolo e neng e ts’episitsoe e ile eaba oela esale ka meso
  54,39,"“Kahoo, latsoang kahlolo ea Ka le temoso ea Ka!”"
  54,40,Ruri Re entse Qura’n ho ba bobebe ho utloisiseha le ho hopoleha; joale na ho teng ea tlang ho amohela temoso
  54,41,"Sechabeng sa Faro, le teng ho ile ha fihla Balemosi (ho tsoa ho Allah)"
  54,42,"Ba ile ba nyelisa Lits’enolo tsa Rona kaofela. Empa Ra ba otla ka kotlo ea Ea Matla Oohle, Ea phethahatsang Thato ea Hae"
  54,43,Mahana-Tumelo a hau ba molemo ho feta bao? Kapa ba na le ts’ireletso kahar’a Lengolo le Halalelang
  54,44,"Kapa ba re: “Rona re lebotho le hlometseng?”"
  54,45,"Haufi Mabotho ohle a tla hloptjoa, a tla supa ntoa ka lirethe"
  54,46,"Che, Hora (ea kahlolo) ke nako ea pallo; Hora eo etla ba e mahlonoko, ebileng eleng bohla"
  54,47,"Ruri ba sebeng ke bona ba lahlehtsoeng ke monahano, ba ea hlanya"
  54,48,"Letsatsi leo ka lona ba tlang ho huleloa ka har’a mollo ka lifahleho,(ba tla utloa): “Utloang lelakabe la Lihele.”"
  54,49,Ruri! Re hlotse lintho tsohle ka tekanyetso
  54,50,"Taelo ea Rona e `ngoe feela, e joaloka ho panya ha leihlo"
  54,51,Re ile Ra ripitla bana ba bo-lona mehleng ea pele; joale na ho teng ea tlang ho amohela temoso
  54,52,Ntho e ngoe le e ngoe eo ba e etsang e teng kahar’a Lengolo
  54,53,"Ntho e ngoe le e ngoe e nyenyane, kapa e kholo e tlalehiloe"
  54,54,Haele ba lokileng ba tla phela kahar’a Lirapa le Linoka
  54,55,"Kahar’a ‘Moka oa ‘Nete, kapel’a Ea Matla Oohle"
  55,1,Ramehauhelo
  55,2,Ke Eena ea rutileng Qura’n
  55,3,U hlotse motho
  55,4,U mo rutile puo
  55,5,Letsatsi le ngoeli li latela tsela ea tsona
  55,6,Lihlahla le lifate – bobeli li ithapalatsa tlas’a Allah
  55,7,U phahamiselitse Leholimo holimo-limo; A ba a ts’epamisa molao
  55,8,Hore le tle le se ke la tlola molao
  55,9,Latelang molao ka hloko kantle le botloko-tsebe
  55,10,U batalalitse lefats’e molemong oa libopuoa tsa Hae
  55,11,Leo holim’a lona ho nang le litholoana le lifate tsa palema tse hlahisang litholoana
  55,12,Le lijo-thollo le tsona limela tse monko o monate
  55,13,Ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang
  55,14,U bopile motho ka letsopa joaloka liboptjoa tsa letsopa
  55,15,Lisabonoeng (li-jinn) U li bopile ka mollo o hlokang mosi
  55,16,Ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang
  55,17,"Ke Mong`a ‘nga tse peli tsa Bochabela, le Mong`a ‘nga tse peli tsa Bophirima"
  55,18,Ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang
  55,19,"Etsoe ke Eena ea lokolotseng maoatle a mabeli, hore a kopane"
  55,20,Ho teng moeli lipakeng tsa ona hoo ka bobeli ba ona oo a ke keng a o tlola
  55,21,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,22,Bobeling ba ona ho hlaha liperela le likhetla
  55,23,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,24,"Likepe tseo tse sesang holima leoatle, tse ts’oanang le lithaba ke tsa Hae"
  55,25,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,26,"Mang, kapa mang ea teng mona lefats’eng o tla shoa"
  55,27,"Ho tla sala feela ke boteng ba Mong`a hau, – Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Tlotlehang"
  55,28,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,29,Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lifats’eng li kopa ho Eena. Ka mehla eohle U bonts’a matla a feletseng a Hae
  55,30,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,31,Haufi re tla fana ka qeto litabeng tsa mafats’e a lona bobeli
  55,32,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,33,"Oho lona ‘moka oa Masabonoeng le batho! Haeba le na le matla a ho tsamaea hohle libakeng tsa maholimo le lefats’e, etsang joalo! Ruri! Le ke ke la etsa joalo kantle le taelo ea Rona"
  55,34,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,35,"Khahlanong le lona ho tla romelloa lelakabe la mollo le mosi, le ke ke la phonyoha"
  55,36,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,37,"Mohla leholimo le petsohang ka lehare, le fetoha leba lefubelu ba setlolo –"
  55,38,"Joale, ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,39,Letsatsing leo motho esita le ea sa bonoeng (jinni) ba sa tlong ho botsoa ho latela libe tsa bona
  55,40,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,41,"Baetsalibe ba tla tsebahala ka mats’oao, ebile ba tla tutloa ka moriri le ka maoto"
  55,42,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,43,Sena ke lihele tseo Baetsalibe ba li latolang
  55,44,Ba tla ba loebaloeba metsing a belang
  55,45,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,46,"Empa haele mang, kapa mang ea ts’abang ho tjamela Mong`a hae mohla Letsatsi la kahlolo, ho tla ba teng Lirapa tse peli"
  55,47,"Joale, ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,48,Tse nang le mefuta eohle (ea lifate le limomonane)
  55,49,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,50,Har’a tsona ho na le liliba tse peli tse phallang
  55,51,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,52,Har’a tsona ho tla ba le mefuta eohle ea litholoana ka bobeli
  55,53,"Joale, ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,54,"Kamoo, ba tla phomola holim’a mealo e aliloeng ka mekhahlelo e khabisitsoeng ka Selika, litholoana tsa Lirapa tseo ka bobeli li le haufi le matsoho a bona"
  55,55,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,56,"Kamoo ho teng basetsana ba hloekileng ba es’o kang ba angoa ke tse sa bonoeng (lijinni), kapa banna pele ho bona"
  55,57,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,58,Ba ts’oanang le majoe a lirubi le majoe a mefuta a leoatle ka botle
  55,59,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,60,Na moputso oa botle ha se botle
  55,61,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,62,"Kathoko ho lirapa tsena, ho teng lirapa tse ling tse peli"
  55,63,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,64,Tse makhasi a `mala o motala tlaka-tlaka
  55,65,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,66,Tse nang le liliba tse peli tse kopotsang kahosafeleng
  55,67,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,68,Tse nang le Litholoana le palema le likharenate ka hare ho tsona
  55,69,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,70,"Ho bile ho teng balekane ba lokileng, ba khahlehang, ba batle – –"
  55,71,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,72,"Balekane ba lihlong, ba luutseng likheleng tse lokileng –"
  55,73,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,74,Bao ho seng monna le ha e le tse sa bonoeng tse kileng tsa ba ama pele ho bona –
  55,75,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,76,Ba phomotseng holim’a mealo e metalana le eona meseme e khahlehang
  55,77,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,78,"Lebitso la Mong`a hau le hlohonolofale, Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Tlotlehang"
  56,1,Mohla ketsahalo e phethahalang –
  56,2,Nakong eo ha ho moea o tla thetseha ka ho tla ha eona
  56,3,E tla nyenyefatsa ba bang; ba bang e tla ba phahamisa
  56,4,Mohla lefats’e le tsukutlehang botebong ba lona
  56,5,Lithaba li tla batalla
  56,6,Hoo li tlang ho fetoha lerole
  56,7,Le tla hloptjhoa ka maquloana a mararo
  56,8,"Joale, sehlopha sa pele sa balekane ba letsohong le letona; – e be sehlopha seo etla be ele se joang"
  56,9,"E be sehlopha sa balekane ba letsoho le lets’ehali, ebe se ka letsohong le lets’ehali etlabe ele se joang"
  56,10,"Joale, ho latele sehlopha se ipabotseng, bao etla ba bona ba ipabotseng (Bophelong Bo-tlang)"
  56,11,Bao ke bona ba tla atamela haufinyane le Allah
  56,12,Kahar’a Lirapa tsa Nyakallo
  56,13,Ho tla be ho kopane mats’oele-ts’oele a batho ba khale-khale
  56,14,Le ba fokolang ba mengoaha ea morao-rao
  56,15,Ba tla be ba lutse holim’a Literone tse khabisitsoeng
  56,16,Le hona ho phomola ba shebane mahlong
  56,17,Ba tla be ba feptjoa ke bacha ho ea kahosafeleng
  56,18,Ka lijana le mepoptjoana e tletseng metsi a liliba tse kopotsang
  56,19,A ke keng a ba bakela ho opeloa ke hlooho le hona ho angoa ke botahoa
  56,20,Ba feptjoa le ka litholoana tseo ba li thabelang
  56,21,Le nama ea linonyana tseo ba li laba-labelang
  56,22,"Ho tla ba teng basali ba ratehang, ba bileng ba mahlo a ncho- cho"
  56,23,Ba joaloka mahakoe a patehileng kahar’a likhaketlana
  56,24,Tseo tsohle e le moputso oa tseo ba neng ba li etsa
  56,25,"Kamoo teng, ba ke ke ba utloa lipuo tse hlohlonts’ang litsebe le tsona lits’okelano"
  56,26,"Haese feela litumeliso tsa: “khotso! Khotso”"
  56,27,Sehlopha balekane ba letsoho le letona; ebe sehlopha seo e tla be e le se joang
  56,28,Se tla ba har’a lifate tsa leoka tse hlokang metsu
  56,29,Ba bile ba le har’a lifate tsa lipalesa tse ririellaneng
  56,30,Tse fanang ka moriti o pharaletseng
  56,31,Ba le har’a liliba tse kollang
  56,32,Le har’a litholoana ka mefuta
  56,33,"Tseo nako ea tsona e sa emiseng, kapa hona ho haneloa ka tsona"
  56,34,Ba tla be ba lutse holim’a mealo e phahamisitsoeng
  56,35,Hobane Ruri! Re ba hloletse balekane ba khethehileng
  56,36,Le hona ho ba etsa ba hloekileng
  56,37,"Ba ratehang, ba lilemong tse lekaneng"
  56,38,Molemong oa ba tla beng ba le ka letsohong le letona
  56,39,E tla be ele mats’oele-ts’oele a batho ba khale-khale
  56,40,Le mats’oele-ts’oele a mengoaha ea morao-rao
  56,41,"Joale, e be ho latela sehlopha se ka letsohong le lets’ehali: ebe sehlopha se ka letsohong le lets’ehali sona ke se joang"
  56,42,"Seo etla ba sehlopha se kahar’a phefo ea mocheso, le metsi a belang"
  56,43,Se bileng se leng kahar’a moriti oa Mosi o Mots’o
  56,44,"O sa pholang, kapa hona ho bata"
  56,45,"Hobane Pele ho mona, ba ne ba sitsitsoe ka nyakallo"
  56,46,Ba ile ba phehella ho kena sebeng se ts’abehang sa ho kopanya Allah le batlatsetsi
  56,47,"Ba ne ba tloaetse ho re: “Na ha re se re shoele re fetohile lerole le masapo, na ka nete re ka boela ra tsosoa hape"
  56,48,Le bo-ntat’a rona moholo?”
  56,49,"E re: “Ruri! batho ba khale-khale le ba mengoaha ea morao- rao"
  56,50,Ba tla khobokangoa ‘moho ts’episong ea letsatsi la pallo
  56,51,"Lona ba etsang bobe, ba bile ba nyefola Tsoho ea Bafu"
  56,52,Ruri! Le tla ja sefate se bitsoang Zaqqum
  56,53,Seo le tla tlatsa limpa ka sona
  56,54,Le tla noa metsi a belang kamora’o ho moo
  56,55,Le tla noa joaloka likamele tse nyoriloeng.”
  56,56,Sena e tla ba kamohelo ea bona ka Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  56,57,Ke Rona ba le hlotseng. Na le tla ke le amohele ‘nete
  56,58,Na le se le ile la bona lithere tsa lona
  56,59,"Ana ke lona ba li hlotseng, kapa ke Rona bahloli ba tsona"
  56,60,"Ke Rona ba faneng ka karolo ea lefu har’a lona, Re ke ke Ra sitoa"
  56,61,Hore Re fetolele libopeho tsa lona ho seo le sa se tsebeng
  56,62,"Ruri le tseba tlholeho ea mathomo. Joale, ke hobaneng ha le sa ketek lithoriso tsa Hae"
  56,63,Na le se le ile la bona peo eo le e jalang
  56,64,"Na ke lona ba e holisang, kapa ke Rona baholisi"
  56,65,"Hoja e bile Thato ea Rona, Ruri! Re ka be Re e ripitlile; le ne le ke ke la khaotsa ho lla ka hore"
  56,66,“Ruri! Re setse ka mejaro ea mekoloto holim’a ho se letho
  56,67,"Che, empa re buselitsoe morao!”"
  56,68,Na le bona metsi ao le’a noang
  56,69,"Na ke lona ba etsang hore a theohe marung, kapa ke Rona ba etsang hore a theohe marung"
  56,70,"Hoja e ne e le thato ea Rona, Re ne Re tla etsa hore a be bohla. Joale, hobaneng ha le sa fane ka liteboho"
  56,71,Na le se le ile la bona mollo oo le o besang
  56,72,"Na ke lona ba ileng ba melisa lifate lefats’eng, kapa ke Rona ba li melisang"
  56,73,"Etsoe Rona, ke Rona ba hlapants’itseng Qura’n e le sehopotso le khotsofalo molemong oa baahi ba lehoatateng le bohle lefats’eng"
  56,74,"Ka lebaka leo, u rorise lebitso la Mong`a hau, Ea Moholo- holo"
  56,75,"Che, ke bitsa bopaki ho likela ha Linaleli –"
  56,76,Seo ke kano e kholohali hoja ebe le ne le tsebile –
  56,77,Sena ke Qura‘n e hlomphehang ka ho fetisisa
  56,78,Ka har’a Lengolo le hlokometsoeng ka tieo
  56,79,"Eo ho seng mang, kapa mang ea ka e amang ntle le ba hloekileng"
  56,80,Ts’enolo e tsoang ho Mong`a Mafats’e
  56,81,Na ke Molaetsa oo le o nyefolang
  56,82,"Le entse tsela ea lona ea bophelo, ho e shanofatsa"
  56,83,"Joale, hobaneng nakong eo moea o nyolohelang ‘metsong oa motho ea shoang le sa thusetse"
  56,84,Empa ebile ka nako eo le ntse le shebile –
  56,85,"Empa Re le haufi haholo ho eena ho feta lona, empa le sa bone –"
  56,86,Hobaneng ha le sa ikamahanye le Rona
  56,87,Ha le busetse moea oo morao ha feela eba le buoa ‘nete
  56,88,"Joale, ke kahoo e reng haeba ele e mong oa ba haufinyane le Allah"
  56,89,"E be oa phela, a be a fumane khotsofalo le Serapa sa Nyakallo"
  56,90,Haeba e le e mong oa ba ka Letsohong le Letona
  56,91,"Joale, kemoo tumeliso ea ba ka letsohong le letona e tla ba: “Khotso e be le uena.”"
  56,92,"Empa haeba e le oa ba nyefoli, ba khelohileng"
  56,93,Kamohelo ea hae e tla ba ea metsi a belang
  56,94,Le hona ho cha Mollong oa Lihele
  56,95,Sena ke ‘nete ea sebele
  56,96,"Kahoo, u rorise lebitso la Mong`a hau, Ea Moholo-holo"
  57,1,"Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng ha li phatlalatse Lithoriso le Boholo ba Allah; hobane ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Seli"
  57,2,"Puso ea maholimo le lefats’e ke tsa Hae; Ke Eena ea fanang ka Bophelo le Lefu, U Matla holim’a lintho tsohle"
  57,3,"Ke Eena oa pele le oa ho Qetela, Ea kantle le kahare; U na le Tsebo e feletseng ea lintho tsohle"
  57,4,"Ke Eena ea hlotseng maholimo le lefats’e ka matsatsi a ts’eletseng; U tsepame Teroneng. U tseba lintho tsohle tse kenang kahar’a lefats’e le tsohle tse tsoang ho lona, le lintho tsohle tse theohelang lefats’eng tse tsoang marung le tsohle tse nyolohelang ho ona; U na le lona hohle moo le leng teng. Ruri! Allah U bona lintho tsohle tseo le li etsang"
  57,5,"Puso ea maholimo le lefats’e ke ea Hae, lintho tsohle li tla boela ho Allah"
  57,6,"Ke Eena ea etsang hore bosiu bo sehe mots’ehare tsebe, ke Eena ea etsang hore mots’ehare o sehe bosiu tsebe; U tseba ka botlalo liphiri tsohle tse ka lifubeng"
  57,7,"Kholoang ho Allah le ho Moromuoa oa Hae le senyeheloe (nyehelo) ka tseo a le nehileng tsona e le lefa; ho ba-kholoang, ba bile ba nyehela; Moputso oa bona ke o babatsehang"
  57,8,Molato oa lona ke eng ha le sa kholoe ho Allah? Empa Moromuoa a le memela ho kholoa ho Mong`a lona; ruri o thehile selekane le lona haeba le banna ba tumelo
  57,9,"Ke Eena ea rometseng Ts’enolo e hlakileng ho lekhabunyane la Hae hore a tle A le inole lefifing la bo-nka-ntjana A le lebise leseling; Ruri Allah U Tletse Khauhelo, Mosa ho lona batho"
  57,10,"Molato oa lona ke eng haele moo le sa senyeheloe ke letho tseleng ea Allah, hobane mafa ohle a maholimo le lefats’e kea Allah? Ba ileng ba senyeheloa esita le hona ho loana pele ho tlholo, ha ba boemong bo lekanang le ba bangata ba lona. Ba boemong bo phahameng ho feta ba ilengba senyeheloa le hona ho loana kamorao. Empa Allah U ts’episitse moputso o babatsehang ho mahlakore ka bobeli. Etsoe Allah U tseba ka botlalo lintho tseo le li etsang"
  57,11,"Ke mang ea tla fana ka kalimo ho Allah ea mokitlane o babatsehang, hore A tle A phaelle mokitlane oo habeli molemong oa hae; moputso oa hae etle ebe o babatsehang"
  57,12,"Ka letsatsi le leng u tla bona banna le basali ba-kholoang ka khanya e phatsimang kapel’a bona ekasitana le ka matsohong a bona a matona; (tumeliso ea bona e le): “Litaba tse molemo ho lona kajeno: Lirapa tseo ka tlasa tsona ho phallang linoka, le tla phela teng kahosafeleng. Ruri! Sena ke katleho e babatsehang.”"
  57,13,"Ka letsatsi le leng Baikaketsi – banna le basali ba re ho Ba- kholoang: “Re emeleng! Re kalimeng khanya ea lona!’ Ho tla thoe:” Khutlelang morao! joale le ilo batla khanya!” Kahoo lerako le tla ahoa lipakeng tsa bona, le nang le mokoallo. Kahar’e ho lona ho tla ba le Mosa o khaphatsehang, kantle ho lona, ho iphaphatha ka lona e tla ba kotlo"
  57,14,"(Ba kantle ho lona) ba tla hoelehetsa, “ana re ne re se ‘moho?” Ba-kholoang ba tla re: “Ruri! Ho bile joalo, empa le ile la thetsana, le hona ho ba leqe le ho ba le khoao; litakatso li ile tsa le isa le khongoana holimo ho fihlela taelo ea Allah e phethahalitsoe; mothetsi a le thetsitse khahlanong le Allah"
  57,15,"Joale, kajeno ha ho mats’eliso a tla amoheloa ho lona le hoba ileng ba nyefola. Lehae la lona ke mollong; seo ke sona sebaka se le loketseng, ebile ele pheletso e nyonyehang ea leeto.”"
  57,16,"Nako ha e so ho fihle sebakeng sa Ba-kholoang hore lipelo tsa bona li thohothelle ka boikokobetso khopolong ea Allah le ka ‘Nete e senotsoeng, bat le ba se ts’oane le ba ileng banehoa Ts’enolo pele, empa nako e telele e ile ea feta eaba lipelo tsa bona lia thatafala? Hobane ba bangata ba bona ke Mahana- puso a batloli ba molao"
  57,17,"Tsebang lona (bohle) hore Allah U fana ka bophelo ho lefats’e kamor’a komello. Re manolotse lits’enolo tsa Rona, hore le tle le ithute bohlale"
  57,18,"Ho ba fanang ka linyehelo, ba bile ba kalima Allah kalimo e babatsehang, kalimo eo ea bona e tla menahangoa ha beli molemong oa bona, bona, moputso oa bona ke o babatsehang"
  57,19,"Bohle ba-kholoang ho Allah le ho moromuoa oa Hae, ba na le tumelo ea sebele; lipaki li ho Mong`a bona, ba bile ba na le moputso le eona khanya, haele ba nyefolang tumelo le hona ho nyefola lits’enolo tsa rona, Bona ke balekane ba Mollo oa Lihele"
  57,20,"Tsebang lona (bohle) hore bophelo ba lefats’e lena empa e le papali feela, boithabiso, boiponahatso, le boikhohomoso har’a lona le hona ho qothisana lehlokoa ka thepa le ka bana; papiso ea bona e ts’oana le ea kholo ea lijalo kamor’a pula hoo li thabisang sehoai, empa kamor’a moo, e be li’a omella li fetole ‘mala li qetelle ese ele mahlaka. Bophelong bo-tlang ho teng kahlolo e nyarosang ho ba ratang bobe, ho teng ts’oarelo ea Allah le monyaka o babatsehang ho ba-kholoang; haele bophelo ba lefats’e lena bona empa e le monyaka oa nakoana"
  57,21,"Le ipehise ho batla ts’oarelo ho Mong`a lona le Serapa seo bolelele ba sona bo lekanang le maholimo le lefats’e, se boloketsoeng bohle ba tlang ho kholoa ho Allah le ho moromuoa oa Hae. Ruri! Eo ke nala ea Allah, eo a sitsang mang, kapa mang ea khahloang ke eena, etsoe nala ea Allah ke e khaphatsehang"
  57,22,"Ha ho bomalimabe bo ka etsahalang lefats’eng kapa meeng ea lona, empa e ngoloa fats’e ka har’a molao pele Re se phethahatsa: Seo se bobebe ho Allah –"
  57,23,"Hore le se nyahame ka litaba tse le etsahallang, kapa la nyakalla ka lereko leo Allah A le sitsang ka tsona, hobane allah ha A rate baikhohomsi"
  57,24,"Batho ba joalo ke ba khoaelang le hona ho khothaletsa batho ho khoaela. Mang, kapa mang ea koenehelang tseleng ea Allah, Ruri! Allah ha A hloke letho. U ts’oanetsoe ke lithoriso tsohle"
  57,25,"Re romeletse baromuoa ba Rona ka Lits’upiso tse Hlakileng le hona ho ba senolela Lengolo le molao, hore batho ba tle ba phethahatse toka; U senotse ts’epe e nang le matla a ts’abehang le melemo e mengata molemong oa batho, hore Allah A tle A tsebe ba mo thusang ‘moho le baromuoa ba hae sephiring. Hobane Allah U Matla Oohle, U Matla a hlollang"
  57,26,"Re ile ra romella Nooe le Abrahama, Ra matlafatsa litloholo tsa bona ka Boporofeta le ka Lengolo, har’a bona ho teng ba tsamaeang ka nepo, empa bongata e bile baetsalibe"
  57,27,"Eaba Re ba hlahlamisa ka baromuoa ba rona metsamaong ea bona; Re ile Ra etsa hore Jesu mora oa Maria a ba latele le hona ho mo neha Evangeli, eaba Re matlafatsa lipelo tsa bohle ka lerato le mohau ba neng ba mo setse morao. Empa ba ile ba iqapela mokhoa oa ho se nyale oo Re sa kang Ra ba laela ona, e le mokhoa oa ho batla monyaka oa Allah; empa ha ba o phethahatse ka ho otloloha. Kahoo, Re fana ka moputso ho ba-kholoang har’a bona, empa bongata ba bona ke baetsalibe"
  57,28,"Oho lona ba-kholoang!Ts’abang Allah, le kholoe ho moromuoa oa Hae. Allah U tla le neha mohau oa Hae o menahantsoe ha beli, ebile U tla le neha khanya eo le tlang ho tsamaea holim’a eona le hona ho le ts’oarelo. Hobane Ruri! Allah U Ts’oarela joalo-joalo, U Tletse Mohau"
  57,29,"Lona batho ba Lengolo le lokela ho tseba hore le ke ke la laola nala ea Allah, nala eohle e kahar’a liatla tsa Allah; U fana ka eona ho mang, kapa mang eo a khahloang ke eena. Allah ke Mong’a Mohau o Khaphatsehang"
  58,1,"Ruri Allah U ile A utloa taba ea mosali ea neng a pheha khang le uena malebana le monna oa hae esita le hona ho tletleba thapelong ho Allah. ‘Allah U utloile khang ea lona. Hobane Ruri Allah U utloa tsohle, U bona tsohle"
  58,2,"Haeba ho teng har’a lona banna ba hlalang basali ba bona ka hore: ba ts’oana le bo-’ma bona, e ke ke ea eba bo-’ma bona; bo-’ma bona ke babats’oetseng – Ruri! ba buoa lentsoe le nyonyehang le lona leshano. Ruri Allah U Ts’oarela joalo- joalo, U Tletse Mohau"
  58,3,"Empa ba hlalang basali ba bona ka hore ba ts’oana le bo-’ma bona, kamor’a moo ebe ba boela ho bona: kahlolo tabeng e joalo ke hore ba lokolle lekhoba pele ba ka amana. Sena ke keletso eo le e filoeng; Allah U tseba ka botlalo lintho tseo le li etsang"
  58,4,"Haeba ho ea hlokang mokhoa oa ho lokolla lekhoba, o lokela ho etsa boitimo ba likhoeli tse peli tse tletseng pele a ka amana le mosali eo; haeba ho na le ea sitoang ho itima, kahlolo ke hore a fepe mafutsana a mashome a ts’eletseng. Sena se etsoa hore le tle le bonts’e tumelo ho Allah ka tieo le ho moromuoa oa Hae. Tsena ke lipallo tse fanoeng ke Allah; mahana-tumelo bona kahlolo ea bona ke e mahlonoko"
  58,5,"Haele bohle ba hanyetsang Allah le Moromuoa oa Hae, ba tla tlontlolloa joaloka ba bileng teng pele ho bona; etsoe Re romeletse lits’upiso tse hlakileng lefats’eng, bahanyetsi bona kahlolo ea bona ke e soabisang"
  58,6,"Letsatsing leo ka lona Allah a tlang ho ba tsosa kaofela, ebe U ba bonts’a ‘nete ea tseo ba neng ba li etsa. Ruri! Allah U bolokile tlaleho ha bona ba e lebetse. Allah ke Paki holim’a lintho tsohle"
  58,7,"Na ha le es’o bone hore Allah U tseba lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng? Ha ho batho ba bararo ba ka itherang sephiring, e be Eena ha se oa bone, kapa ebe ba bahlano, Eena ke oa botselela, kapa ebe ba ka tlase ho lipalo tseo kapa le ho ba kaholim’a tsona, empa U teng har’a bona hohle moo ba teng; kamor’a moo mohla Letsatsi la Tsoho, U tla ba tsebisa tsohle tseo ba neng ba li etsa. Ruri! Allah ke Paki ea lintho tsohle"
  58,8,"Na ha le es’o bone batho ba hanetsoeng ho ithera lekunutung, bao hamorao ba boelang ho seo ba ileng ba se haneloa, ebe joale ba ithera hammoho ho tlola molao le hona ho etsa lintho tse nyonyehang le hona ho se mamele moromuoa? Joale, nakong eo ba tlang ho uena ebe ba u lumelisa ka tumeliso eo Allah a es’ong ho u lumelise ka eona, e be ba re: “Joale, ke hobaneng ha Allah A sa re ahlolele seo re se buileng?” Ruri! Lihele li balekane, ba tla utloa mocheso oa tsona – Ruri! Pheletso e nyonyehang ea leeto"
  58,9,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Haeba le ithera hammoho, le se ke la ithera ka tlolo ea molao le bona bora le ho se mamele moromuoa, empa le ithere hammoho ka toka le mosa; le ts’abe Allah Eo le tlang ho bokelleloa ho Eena"
  58,10,"Boithero ba lekunutung ke mesebetsi ea Ea Mobe, hore a tle a khopise ba-kholoang; empa a ke ke a ba khopisa ka letho kantle le haeba e le thato ea Allah. Ba-kholoang ba behe ts’epo ea bona ho Allah"
  58,11,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Ha ho thoe ho lona le bule sebaka ‘mokeng, le se bule; Allah U tla le etsetsa sebaka bophelong bo-tlang. Ha ho thoe ho lona, le potlake ha le’a thapelong, le potlake; Allah U tla phahamisetsa ba-kholoang har’a lona le ba nang le tsebo maemong a phahameng. Ruri! Allah U tseba ka botlalo tseo le li etsang"
  58,12,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Nakong eo le nang le lipuisano le Moromuoa, le fane ka linyehelo pele ho lipuisano tsa lona. Seo se molemo, ebile se hloekile molemong oa lona. Empa haeba le hloka mokhoa oa ho fana ka linyehelo, Allah U Ts’oarela joalo-joalo, U Tletse Mohau"
  58,13,"Na le ts’aba ho fana ka linyehelo pele ho lipuisano? Joale, haeba le sa etse seo; ‘Allah A le nehile ts’oarelo, phethahatsang lithapelo le be le fane ka linyehelo tsa mafutsana le hona ho mamela Allah le Moromuoa oa Hae. Allah U hlokolosi ka lintho tseo le li etsang"
  58,14,"Na u se u ile oa bona batho ba thehang setsoalle le bao khalefo ea Allah e leng holim’a bona? Ha ho kamano har’a lona le bona, kapa kamano har’a bona le lona, ba ikana ka kano ea leshano ka tsebo e feletseng"
  58,15,Allah U ba lokiselitse kahlolo e ts’abehang. Tse nyonyehang ke tsohle tseo ba tloaetseng ho li etsa
  58,16,"Ba entse likano tsa bona sekhurumetso le hona ho khelosa batho tseleng ea Allah; kahoo, kahlolo ea bona ke e soabisang"
  58,17,Thepa le bana ba bona ha ho kamoo ba ka ba thusang kateng khahlanong le Allah. Ka kotloloho ke balekane ba mollo; ba tla phela kamoo kahosafeleng
  58,18,"Ka letsatsi le leng Allah U tlaba tsosa kaofela, na ba tla ikana ho Eena joaloka ha ba etsa ho lona masolomane, ba tla nahana hore ba na le sekhurumetso seo ba tla its’ireletsa ka sona. Ruri! Na ha se bona ba leshano"
  58,19,"Ba busoa ke Ea Mobe, o entse hore ba lebale Allah. Ke mokhoa oa liabolosi. Ruri! Ana ha se mokha oa Ea Mobe o tla lahleha"
  58,20,"Haele bohle ba hanyetsang Allah le moromuoa oa Hae, ba tla ba har’a ba tlontlolotsoeng"
  58,21,"Allah U fane ka taelo hore: “Ruri! Ke ‘Na ea tla hapa tlholo, ‘Na le baromuoa ba Ka”. Hobane Ruri! Allah U Matla a hlollang, U phethahatsa Thato ea Hae"
  58,22,"Ruri! U ke ke oa bona batho ba-kholoang ho Allah le ho letsatsi la bofelo ba rata bahanyetsi ba Allah le moromuoa oa Hae, le ha ekaba bo-ntat’a bona, bara ba bona le bana ba bo-bona le leloko la bona. Ba joalo Allah U ngotse tumelo lipelong tsa bona, U bile U ba matlafalitse ka moea o halalelang o tsoang ho Eena, U tla ba amohella kahar’a lirapa tse ts’akhunyang linoka, ebile ba tla phela kahar’a tsona ka ho sa feleng. Allah U nyakaletse ke bona, le bona ba nyakaletse ke Eena. Oo ke mokha oa Allah. Ruri! Ana ha se mokha oa Allah U atlehileng"
  59,1,"Tsohle tse maholimong le lefats’eng, ha li bolele Lithoriso le Boholo ba Allah, Hobane U Matla Oohle, U Seli"
  59,2,"Ke Eena Ea ileng A etsa hore Mahana-tumelo har’a batho ba Lengolo ba phaphatheha malapeng a bona ho ea kholehong ea pele. Le ne le sa nahane hore ba tla phaphatheha, ba ne ba nahana hore liqhobosheane tsa bona li tla ba ts’ireletsa khahlanong le Allah. Empa Khalefo ea Allah e ile ea finyella ho bona ka lesoba leo ba neng ba sa le lebella, A kenya letsoalo lipelong tsa bona hoo ba ileng ba ripitla malapa a bona ka matsoho a bona le a ba-kholoang. Oho lona ba nang le mahlo! Kahoo, inkeleng khalemo"
  59,3,"Hoja ebe Allah ha A ka A ba laela ho phaphateha, Ruri! A ka be A ba ahlotse lefats’eng lena; bophelong Bo-tlang kahlolo ea bona e tlaba Mollo"
  59,4,"Seo ke hobane ba le khahlanong le Allah le Moromuoa oa Hae; mang kapa mang ea khahlanong le Allah, Ruri! Kotlo ea Allah ke e nyarosang"
  59,5,"Hore na ke lifate tse kae tsa palema tseo le li rathang, kapa le li lesa li ntse li eme, ke ka tumello ea Allah, hore A tle A apese mahana-puso ka tlontlollo"
  59,6,"Tseo Allah A sitsitseng Moromuoa oa Hae ka tsona ho tsoa ho bona – , hore le li fumane kantle le ho kalla lipere, kapa likamele tsa lona eaba le ba khahlela ka tsona; empa Allah U fana ka matla ho Moromuoa oa Hae holim’a mang, kapa mang ea khahloang ke eena. Ebile Allah U na le Matla holima lintho tsohle"
  59,7,"Tseo Allah A sitsitseng Moromuoa oa Hae ka tsona ho tsoa ho baahi ba metse, – ke tsa Allah – le moromuoa oa Hae, beng ka eena, likhutsana, mafutsana le bahahlaoli; hore li tle li se ke tsa laoloa ke morui e mong har’a lona a li etsa tsa hae. Ntho efe, kapa efe eo moromuoa a le nehang eona le e nke; ka ho ts’oana le eo a le hanelang ka eona, le e lese. Le be le ts’abe Allah. Hobane kotlo ea Allah ke e nyarosang"
  59,8,"Ho mafutsana a baphaphathehi (Muhajirs) ba phalalisitsoeng malapeng a bona le thepeng ea bona, ha ba ntse ba tsomana le nala ea Allah le mohau oa Hae le hona ho thusa Allah le Moromuoa oa Hae: Bao ke bona ba nang le ‘nete"
  59,9,"Empa ba bileng le malapa pele ho bona (Al-Madina), ba amohela tumelo ba bonts’a lerato ho ba ileng ba baleha eaba ba fumana bots’abeli ho bona, ebile lipelong tsa bona ba hloka takatso ea lintho tseo ba li filoeng; ba li tella ba phaphathehi ba teng ho bona ho sa tsotellehe hore na bona ba lapa ho le ho kae. Mang, kapa mang ea pholohileng ho ba meharo – Ruri! bao ke ba atlehileng"
  59,10,"Bohle ba amohetseng tumelo kamor’a bona ba re: “Mong`a rona! U re ts’oarele le bana ba bo-rona ba bileng teng pele ho rona tumelong ena, U tlose mohono lipelong tsa rona khahlanong le ba-kholoang. Mong`a rona! Ruri! Ke Uena Ea Tletseng Mosa, Ea Mohau o Khaphatsehang.”"
  59,11,"Na ha u es’o bone kamoo Baikaketsi ba buoang kateng ho bana ba bo-bona ba hanang tumelo har’a batho ba Lengolo: “Haeba le ka phalalisoa, Ruri! Re tla phaphatheha le lona; re ke ke ra mamela mang, kapa mang ea khahlano le lona, ebile re tla le thusa haeba le ka tsometsoa. Ruri! Allah ke paki hore ba buoa leshano"
  59,12,"Haeba ba ka phalalisoa ba ke ke ba phaphatheha le bona le hona ho ba thusa haeba ba ka tsometsoa; le ha ba ne ba ka thusetsa, ba ne ba tla ba supa ka lirethe, kahoo ba ke ke ba fumana thuso"
  59,13,"Ka ‘nete le matla ho ba feta ka lebaka la ts’abo e lipelong tsa bona, e rometsoeng ke Allah. Sena ke hobane e le batho ba hlokang kutloisiso"
  59,14,"Ba ke keba le loants’a le ha ba le ‘moho kantle le haeba ba le kahar’a lihaelo tse ts’irelelitsoeng ka tieo, kapa eba ba kamor’a marako. Moea oa ntoa o mo ngata ha ba le bang: u ka nahana hore ba ipopile, empa lipelo tsa bona li fapane. Hobane ke batho ba hlokang bohlale"
  59,15,"Ba ts’oana le ba bileng teng pele ho bona, ba latsoitse litla- morao tse mpe tsa liketso tsa bona; sebakeng sa bona ho na le Kahlolo e mahlonoko;- –"
  59,16,"Joaloka ka ea Mobe, ha a re ho motho,” Latola Allah”: empa ha motho a latola Allah,(Ea Mobe) O re,” ‘Na ke thoko le uena. Ke ts’aba Allah, Mong`a Mafats’e!”"
  59,17,"Pheletso ea bona ke e ts’oanang ka bobeli, ba tla phela kahar’a mollo ka ho sa feleng. Oo ke oona moputso oa baetsalibe"
  59,18,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Ts’abang Allah. Le be le lese moea ofe kapa ofe ho iponela seo o se behileng nale bokamosong. Ts’abang Allah: Hobane Allah U tseba ka botlalo tseo le li etsang"
  59,19,"Le se ts’oane le ba lebetseng Allah, bao Allah A entseng hore ba lebale meea ea bona. Bao ke mahana-puso a tlotseng meeli"
  59,20,"Ha ho tekano lipakeng tsa Balekane ba Mollo le Balekane ba Serapa: Ke Balekane ba Serapa, ba tla fihlela Nyakallo"
  59,21,"Hoja e be Re ile Ra senolela Qura’n ena holim’a thaba, Ruri! U ka be u bone ha e ithapalatsa, ebile e petsoha kamoo e ts’abang Allah kateng. Ruri! Re etsa lipapiso tsena molemong oa batho, hore ba tle ba inahane"
  59,22,"Ke Allah, ntle ho Eena ha ho `Mopi e mong, Motsebi oa tse patehileng le tse pepeneneng. Ke Eena Ea Tletseng Lereko, Ea Mohau o Khaphatsehang"
  59,23,"Ke Allah, ntle ho eena ha ho `Mopi e mong, Motlotlehi, Ea Halalelang A Inots’i, Mokolli oa khotso, ‘Moloki oa Tumelo, ‘Maballi oa Ts’ireletso, Ea Matla Oohle, Ea sa Hloloeng ke letho, Ea Phahameng ka ho Fetisisa. Tlotla e be ho Allah, Ea phahametseng tsohle tseo ba mo bapisang le tsona"
  59,24,"Ke Allah, ‘Mopi, Moqapi oa tsohle, Mofani oa Sebopeho. Mabitso oohle a matle ho fetisisa ke’ A Hae. Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng li’a mo Tlotlisa, U Matla Oohle, U Seli"
  60,1,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Le se thehe setsoalle le lira tsa Ka le tsona lira tsa lona, – Na le ka theha setsoalle le bona joang, empa ba sa lumele ‘nete eo le e senoletsoeng le hona ho phalalisa Moromuoa ‘moho le lona malapeng a lona hobane le kholoa ho Allah? Haeba le tloha malapeng a lona ho ea loanela tsela ea Ka le hona ho batla monyaka o molemo oa Ka, le se ke la theha setsoalle le bona. Na le bonts’a setsoalle ho bona sephiring, empa e le ‘Na ea hlokolosi ka ho fetisisa ka tseo le li patang le tseo le li pepesang? Mang, kapa mang ea etsang joalo har’a lona, Ruri! O khelohile tseleng e topileng"
  60,2,"Ha ba ka le okamela, e tla ba lira tsa lona le hona ho nanabetsa matsoho le maleme a bona khahlanong le lona ka morero o nyonyehang: takatso ea bona ke hore le latole ‘nete"
  60,3,"Haele beng ka lona le bana ba lona, ba ke ke ba le thusa ka letho mohla Letsatsi la Kahlolo: U tla ahlola lipakeng tsa lona; Hobane Allah U bona tsohle tseo le li etsang"
  60,4,"Ho teng mohlala o motle haholo molemong oa lona ka Abrahama le ba neng ba ena le eena, mohla ba neng ba re ho batho ba habo bona: “Ruri! Rona ha re na molato ho lona le ho tsohle tseo le li khumamelang ntle ho Allah. Re’a le latola. Ho tsohile lehloeo lipakeng tsa rona le lona ho fihlela le khotsoe ho Allah A Inots’i” – kantle le puo eo Abrahama a ileng a e tsepisa ntata’e ea hore: “ke tla u kopela ts’oarelo, le hoja ke hloka taolo holima tsohle kapel’a Allah” ba rapela “Mong`a rona! Re behile ts’epo ea rona ho uena, re sokolohela ho uena joaloka ha ho uena e le pheletsong"
  60,5,"“Mong`a rona! Se re etse teko malebana le mahana-tumelo, Empa re ts’oarele, Mong’a rona! Ke Uena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Seli.”"
  60,6,"Ho teng mohlala ho bona sebakeng sa lona ho o latela, – ho bao ts’epo ea bona e leng ho Allah le Letsatsi la Bofelo. Empa ha mang, kapa mang a koeneha, Ruri! Allah ha A hloke letho, U ts’oaneloa ke Lithoriso tsohle"
  60,7,"Kamohlomong Allah U tla theha lerato lipakeng tsa lona le lira tsa lona. Hobane Allah U Matla Oohle; ebile U Ts’oarela joalo-joalo, U Tletse Mohau"
  60,8,"‘Allah ha A le thibele, ho ba sa le loants’eng malebana le Tumelo le hona ho le phalalisa malapeng a lona, ho sebetsa ka mosa le toka le bona: Hobane Ruri! Allah U rata ba nang le toka"
  60,9,"Allah U khahlanong, le ba le loants’ang ka lebaka la Tumelo le ho le phalalisa malapeng a lona, ba bileba thusana ho le phalalisa. Mang, kapa mang ea tla theha setsoalle le bona – kaofela ha bona ke baetsalibe"
  60,10,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Nakong eo basali ba-kholoang ba phaphathehelang ho lona, le ba hlahlobe: Allah U tseba ka botlalo ka Tumelo ea bona: ha le fumana hore e feela ke ba- kholoang, le se ba khutlisetse morao ho Mahana-tumelo. Hobane ha se basali ba molaong le ho mahana-tumelo le bona mahana-tumelo ha se banna ba molaong ho bona. Le lefe mahana-tumelo mahali ao ba a lefileng holim’a bona. Ha ho molato haeba le ka nyala basali ba joalo, ha feela le ba nehile mahali a bona. Le se ke la nyalana le basali ba sa kholoang, le kope mahali ao le ba nehileng ona, ka ho ts’oana le ba sa kholoang le ba lokollele mahali ao ba a lefileng. Sena ke Molao oa Allah. Ke Eena ea ahlolang lipakeng tsa lona. Etsoe Allah U Tlettse Tsebo, U Seli"
  60,11,"Haeba basali ba bang ba lona ba ka balehela ho mahana- tumelo, eba le na le monyetla(oa mosali ea tlang ho tsoa lehlakoreng la mahana-tumelo), lfang bao basali ba bona ba ngalileng mahali a lekanang le ao ba a lefileng. Le ts’abe Allah Eo le kholoang ho Eena"
  60,12,"Oho Moprofeta! Ha basali ba-kholoang ba tla ho uena, ba ikana ka tieo ho uena hore ba ke ke ba maneha batlatsetsi ho Allah le hona ho utsoa, le hore ba k eke ba etsa bohlola, kapa ho bolaea bana ba bona, kapa ho bua leshano leo a iqapetseng lona, kapa hona ho se u mamele le se lokileng se molaong oa islam, – joale, u amohele boikano ba bona le hona hoba kopela ts’oarelo ho Allah. Hobane Ruri! Allah U Ts’oarela- joalo-joalo, U Tletse Mohau"
  60,13,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Le se ke la theha setsoalle le bao Khalefo Ea Allah e ba tobileng, ba lahlehetsoeng ke ts’epo bophelong Bo-tlang, joaloka Mahana-tumelo ha a lahlehetsoe ke ts’epo ka ba mabitleng"
  61,1,"Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tse lefats’eng, ha li bolele Lithoriso le Boholo Ba Allah, hobane Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Seli"
  61,2,Oho lona ba-kholoang! Hobaneng le buoa seo le sa se phetheng
  61,3,"Ntho eo e nyonyeha hampe mahlong A Allah, ea hore le buoe seo le sa se phethahatseng"
  61,4,Ruri! Allah U rata ba loanelang tsela ea Hae ka mekhahlelo ba ipopele ngatana-ngoe
  61,5,"Hopolang Moshe ha a ne a re ho batho ba habo: “Oho batho ba heso! Hobaneng ha le nkhopisa le nthohaka, empa le tseba hantle hore ke moromuoa oa Allah ho lona?” Joale, ha ba kheloha tseleng e nepahetseng, Allah A khelosa lipelo tsa bona. Hobane Allah ha A tataise mahana-puso a tlolang meeli"
  61,6,"Hopolang Jesu mora oa Maria ha a ne a re: “Oho bana ba Israele! Ke moromuoa oa Allah, ho lona ho hlapants’a Molao o senotsoeng pele ho ‘na kahar’a torah ho le tsebisa litaba tse molemo tsa moromuoa ea tla tla kamorao ho ‘na, eo lebitso la hae e leng Ahmad.” Empa, eitse hoba a finyelle ho bona ka Lits’upiso tse hlakileng, eaba ba re: “Enoa ke moloi ea pepenene.”"
  61,7,Ke mang ea etsang phoso e kholohali haese ea qapang leshano khahlanong le Allah empa a bitselitsoe ho inehela Islamong? Ruri! Allah ha A tataise mahana-puso a tlolang meeli
  61,8,"Takatso ea bona ke ho tima Khanya ea Allah ka melomo ea bona, empa Allah U tla phethahatsa Khanya ea Hae le ha mahana-tumela a e hloile"
  61,9,"Ke Eena ea romeletseng Moromuoa oa Hae ka tataiso le ka Tumelo ea ‘Nete, hore a tle a e phatlalatse kaholim’a litumelo tsohle le ha bahloka tumelo ba e hloile(bahedene)"
  61,10,Oho lona ba-kholoang! Na nka le tataisetsa khoebong e ka le pholosang Timelong e mahlonoko
  61,11,"Hore le kholoa ho Allah le ho Moromuoa oa Hae, le tsitlallela tseleng ea Allah ka thepa le ka maphelo a lona. Seo se molemo ka ho fetisisa ho lona hoja eba le ne le tseba"
  61,12,"‘Allah U tla le ts’oarela libe tsa lona, A be amohelle kahar’a lirapa tseo linoka li phallang tlasa tsona le Matlo a matle kahar’a Lirapa tsa edene. Seo ke katleho e Babatsehang"
  61,13,"Ebile Allah U tla le neha motlopotlo oo le o thabelang: thuso e tsoang ho Allah le tlholo e haufinyane. Kahoo, phatlalatsa litaba tse molemo ho ba-kholoang"
  61,14,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Ebang bathusi ba Allah, joaloka ha Jesu mora oa Maria a ne a re ho barutuoa ba hae: “Ke ba feng bao e tlang ho ba bathusi ba ka tsebeletsong ea Allah?” Barutuoa ba re: “Re bathusi ba Allah.” Joale, lequloana la bana ba Israele le ile la kholoa, ha le leng lona le latola tumelo. Empa, Ra matlafatsa ba khotsoeng khahlano le lira tsa bona, ea eba bahloli"
  62,1,"Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle lefats’eng li bolela Lithoriso le Boholo Ba Allah, – Motlotlehi, Ea Halalelang, Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Seli"
  62,2,"Ke Eena Ea romeletseng har’a ba sa rutehang moromuoa oa habo bona, ho ba phetela Lits’enolo tsa Hae, Ho ba hloekisa le ho ba ruta ka Lengolo le Bohlale, – le hoja pele ho mona ba ne ba le har’a sebe se hlakileng"
  62,3,"Ka ho ts’oana le ba bang ba es’ong ho kopana le bona. Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Seli"
  62,4,"Lena ke lereko la Allah, leo A sitsang mang, kapa mang ea khahloang ke eena ka lona. Allah ke Mong’a lereko le khaphatsehang"
  62,5,"Papiso ea ba ileng ba fumana Molao oa Moshe, eaba ba ea hloleha ho ona, E ts’oana le ea pokola e jereng mangolo a maholo. Papiso e nyonyehang ea ba fetolang Lits’enolo tsa Allah ka mashano. Etsoe Allah ha A tataise batho ba etsang bobe"
  62,6,"E re: “Oho lona ba emeng Bo-Judeng! Haeba le nahana le metsoalle ea Allah, ho qolla lichaba tse ling, joale, ipitsetseng lefu haeba le buoa ‘nete.”"
  62,7,Empa ba ke keba ipiletsa lona ho latela lintho tsohle tseo matsoho a bona a li rometseng nale! Allah U tseba ka botlalo ba etsang bobe
  62,8,"E re: “Lefu leo le le balehang le tla le khahlanyetsa: kamor’a moo le tla boela ho Motsibi oa tse patehileng le tse pepeneneng; kemoo A tlang ho le bolella tsohle tseo le neng le li etsa.”"
  62,9,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Nakong eo le utloang pitso ea thapelo ea khobokano ea letsatsi la Labohlano, le potlakele pitsong ea Allah; le lese likhoebo tsa lona. Seo se molemo ho lona hoja eba le ne le tseba"
  62,10,"Hang ha thapelo e fetile, le ka hasana le naha eohle ho ea batla nala ea Allah; empa le keteke Lithoriso tsa Allah ka ho fetisisa hore le tle le atlehe"
  62,11,"Empa hang ha ba bona khoebo, kapa monyaka ba khothometseha ho ea teng, ba o sie o tjamme. E re: “Tseo Allah A nang le tsona li molemo ho feta boithabiso, kapa khoebo; ke Eena Ea Molemo ho fana"
  63,1,"Ha Baikaketsi ba tla ho uena ba re: “Re paka hore ruri u Moromuoa oa Allah.” Allah U ea tseba hore u Moromuoa oa Hae, ‘Allah ke paki hore ruri Baikaketsi ba bua leshano"
  63,2,"Likano tsa bona ba li entse sets’ireletso, hore ba tle ba khelose batho tseleng ea Allah. Ruri! Liketso tsa bona li ea nyonts’a"
  63,3,"Hobane ba ile ba kholoa hamorao ba koenehela Tumelo; lipelo tsa bona li kabiloe: kahoo ha ba utloisise"
  63,4,"Ha u ba sheba, libopeho tsa bona li’a u khahla; ha ba buoa u’a ba mamela. Ba ts’oana le likutu tsa patsi tse ts’ehelitseng. Ba nahana hore molumo o mong le o mong o khahlanong le bona. Ke lira tsa hau u ba hlokomele. Thohako ea Allah e be holim’a bona! Kamoo ba tsoileng tseleng kateng"
  63,5,"Ha ho thoe ho bona: “Atamelang! Moromuoa oa Allah u tla le kopela ts’oarelo!” Ba thint’sa lifahleho, u tla ba bona ba furalla ka boikhohomoso"
  63,6,"Ho ea ts’oana ho bona le ha u ka ba kopela ts’oarelo, kapa u saba kopeleng, Allah A ke ke a ba ts’oarela. Hobane Ruri! Allah ha A tataise Mahana-puso a tlolang meeli"
  63,7,"Ke bona ba reng: “Le se senyeheloe ke letho ho ba nang le moromuoa oa Allah, ho fihlela ba qhalane ba tsoile Al- Madina;” Empa matlotlo a maholimo le lefats’e ke’a Allah, le hoja Baikaketsi ho se seo ba se utloisisang"
  63,8,"Ba re: “Ruri! Haeba re ka boela Al-Madina, ea matla a fetisisang o tla leleka mofokoli.” Empa matla ke a Allah le Moromuoa oa Hae le ho Ba-kholoang; Empa Baikaketsi ha ba na tsebo"
  63,9,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Le se lumelle maruo le bana ba lona ho le khelosa khopolong ea Allah. Ba tla etsa joalo, ke ba lahlehetsoeng"
  63,10,"Le fane ka matlotlo ao Re le sitsitseng ka ona pele lefu le khahlanyetsa e mong oa lona, a be a re: “Mong`a ka! Ha feela U ka mpa oa nkekeletsa nakoana? Hore ke tle ke fane ka linyehelo; ke tle ke be har’a ba lokileng.”"
  63,11,"Empa Allah a ke ke a fana ka nyehlisetso ho moea ofe, kapa ofe ha feela nako ea pallo e se e fihlile; Allah U hlokolosi ka lintho tseo le li etsang"
  64,1,"Tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng li bolela Lithoriso le Boholo Ba Allah; Eo Puso le thoriso e leng tsa Hae, U matla holima tsohle"
  64,2,"Ke Eena Ea le hlotseng, ba bang ba lona ke mahana-tumelo, ba bang ke Ba-kholoang;’Allah U bona tsohle tseo le li etsang"
  64,3,"U hlotse maholimo le lefats’e ka tekano e nepahetseng, A le neha sebopeho le hona ho le neha libopeho tse ntle, Ruri! Pheletso e ho Eena"
  64,4,"U tseba tse maholimong le tse lefats’eng, U tseba tseo le li patang le tseo le li pepesang. ‘Allah U tseba ka botlalo tse kahar’a lipelo"
  64,5,"Na pale ea ba ileng ba latola tumelo khale e se kile ea fihla ho lona? Ba ile ba latsoa sephetho se bosula sa boits’oaro ba bona, kahlolo ea bona e bile e mahlonoko"
  64,6,"Ke hobane baromuoa ba ‘nile ba fihla ho bona ka lits’upiso tse hlakileng, Empa ba re: “Re ka tataisoa ke motho?” Kahoo, ba ile ba latola eaba ba a furalla; empa Allah ha a hloke letho ho tsoa ho bona. Allah ha A na litlhoko, U Ts’oanetso ke lithoriso"
  64,7,"Mahana-tumelo ba nahana hore ba ke ke ba tsosoa hape. E re: “E, Ruri! Ka Mong`a ka! Le tla boela le tsosoa hape, le tla tsebisoa tsohle tseo le li entseng; hobane seo se bonolo ho Allah.”"
  64,8,Kholoang ho Allah le ho Moromuoa oa Hae le ho Leseli leo Re le senotseng. Allah U hlokolosi ka tsohle tseo le li etsang
  64,9,"Letsatsi leo A tlang ho le bokella Letsatsing la Khobokano, leo e tla be e le letsatsi la tahlehelo le kuno ho ba bangata. Bohle ba ba-Kholoang ho Allah le hona ho etsa toka, Allah U tla hlakola ho bona liketso maloetse le ho ba amohela kahar’a Lirapa tseo linoka li phallang ka tlasa tsona; ba tla phela kamoo kahosafeleng. Seo ke Katleho e Babatsehang"
  64,10,"Empa ba latolang Tumelo le hona ho nyelisa Lits’enolo tsa rona, e tla ba Balekane ba Mollo; ho phela kamoo kahosafeleng – Pheletso e nyonyehang"
  64,11,"Ha ho sekhobo sefe, kapa sefe se ka oang kantle ho tumello ea Allah. Mang, kapa mang ea kholoang ho Allah, Allah U tataisa pelo ea hae. ‘Allah U Tseba tsohle"
  64,12,"Utloang Allah le Moromuoa oa Hae; empa haeba le koeneha, ts’ebetso ea Moromuoa Oa Rona ke feela ho phatlalatsa molaetsa ka ho hlaka"
  64,13,"Allah! Ha ho `Mopi e mong ntle ho Eena. Kahoo, lesang ba- kholoang ba behe ts’epo ea bona ho Eena"
  64,14,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Ruri! Ho teng lira tsa lona har’a basali le bana ba lona, kahoo le ba hlokomele. Empa ha le ts’oarela le tlolisa liphoso tsa bona mahlo le koahela liphoso tsa bona, Ruri Allah U Ts’oarela-joalo-joalo, U Tletse Mohau"
  64,15,"Maruo a lona le bana ba lona e ka ‘na ea eba teko: Empa kapela Allah ho teng Moputso o moholohali"
  64,16,"Kahoo ts’abang Allah ka hohle kamoo le ka khonang, le mamele le be le latele le hona ho nyehela molemong oa meea ea lona. Mang, kapa mang ea pholohileng meharong ea meea ea bona, – Ke bona ba tla fumana katleho"
  64,17,"Ha le etsa kalimo e ntle ho Allah, U tla e menahanya ha beli molemong oa lona le hona ho le ts’oarela, hobane Allah ke mot’soareli oa libe, e bile o na le Mamello e Fetisisang"
  64,18,"Motsibi oa liphiri le tse pepeneneng, Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Seli"
  65,1,"Oho Moporofeta! Ha le hlala basali, ba hlaleng ho latela nako e behiloeng (idda) le bale matsatsi ao ka nepo; le ts’abe Allah, Mong`a lona: Le se baleleke malapeng a bona, kapa hona ho tloha malapeng, kantle le haeba ba molato oa bohlola. Eo ke meeli e fanoeng ke Allah; mang, kapa mang ea ka tlolang meeli ea Allah, Ruri! O fosetsa moea oa hae: Ha o tsebe letho Kamohlomong Allah kamor’a moo U ne A ka ‘na A tlisa maemo a fetohileng"
  65,2,"Ha ba se ba phethisitse pallo ea bona, ba amoheleng ka mosa, kapa le arohane le bona ka mosa; le bitse lipaki tse peli har’a lona, ba nang le toka, bopaki ba lona ebe bo nepahetseng kapel’a Allah. Seo ke tlhokomeliso ho ea kholoang ho Allah le ho Letsatsi la Bofelo. Mang, kapa mang ea ts’abang Allah, Ruri! Allah U mo lokisetsa tsela"
  65,3,"Le hona ho mo sitsa ka seo a neng a sa se lebella ho tsoa mehloling ea Hae. Etsoe mang, kapa mang ea behang ts’epo ea hae ho Allah, Allah U mo lekane. Hobane ruri! Allah U tla phethahatsa taelo ea Hae. Ruri Allah U fane ka pallo ho lintho tsohle"
  65,4,"Haele basali ba lona ba seng ba fetile lilemo tsa bona tsa ho ea matsatsing, haeba le na le khoao, nako ea bona ha e be likhoeli tse tharo ka ho ts’oana le ba sa eeng matsatsing ho hang. Bakhachane; nako ea bona ea pallo ke ho fihlela ba beleha. Mang, kapa mang ea ts’abang Allah, Allah U tla nolofatsa tsela ea hae"
  65,5,"Eo ke Taelo Ea Allah Ea e rometseng ho lona: Ea ts’abang Allah, Allah U tla hlakola maloetse ho eena, A phaelle Moputso oa Hae"
  65,6,"Le phelise basali ka mokhoa oo le phelang ka oona ho latela matla a lona, le se ba khopise e le ho ba thatafaletsa. Haeba ba ithoetse, le ba khokomele ho fihlela ba belehile: Haeba ba le anyesetsa bana ba lona, le ba lefe ka mokhoa o lokelang; le nke qeto ka bobeli. Ha le thatafalloa ke litaba ka bobeli, batlang bo-’m’e monyants’etsi ho nyants’a lesea molemong oa ntata’e"
  65,7,"Le lumelle monna oa morui ho fana ho latela matla hae, ka ho ts’oana le monna ea kojoana-li-mahetleng, mo lumelleng a fane ho latela seo Allah a mo setsitseng ka sona. Allah ha A imetse moea ofe kapa ofe kantle le seo A o nehileng sona. ‘Allah U tla rarolla tsohle"
  65,8,"Ke lichaba tse kae tse bileng khahlanong le taelo ea Mong`a tsona le ba romuoa ba Hae, tseo kamor’a moo li ileng tsa bitsetsoa kahlolong, – ho ba kahlolong? – Ra ba lihela kahlolo e le mohlala ho ba bang"
  65,9,"Li ile tsa latsoa liketso litholoana tse bosula tsa boits’oaro ba tsona, Pheletso ea boits’oaro ba tsona ebile Tahleho"
  65,10,"Allah U ba hlophiselitse kahlolo e ts’abehang; Kahoo, ts’abang Allah lona batho ba nang le kutloisiso-ba Kholoang! Hobane ruri Allah U le romeletse molaetsa"
  65,11,"Moromuoa ea le phetelang Lits’enolo tsa Allah tse nang le manollo e hlakileng, hore a tle a etelle pele ba-kholoang le hona ho etsa liketso tse lokileng, ho tsoa Lefifing a ba lebise Leseling. Ba-kholoang ho Allah le hona ho etsa liketso tse lokileng, Allah U tla ba amohella kahar’a Lirapa tseo linoka li phallang ka tlasa tsona; ho phela kamoo kahosafeleng. Ebile Allah U ba hlophiselitse moputso o babatsehang"
  65,12,"Ke Allah Ea hlotseng Maholimo a supileng le lefats’e ka mokhoa o ts’oanang. Taelo e theohela har’a ona, ele hore le tle le tsebe hore Allah U na le matla holima lintho tsohle; le hore Allah U kopetse lintho tsohle hare ka tsebo"
  66,1,"Oho Moporofeta! Hobaneng ha u hanana le seo Allah a se entseng molao, moo u habileng ho thabisa basali ba hau? Empa Allah U Ts’oarela Khafetsa, U Tletse Mohau"
  66,2,"Ruri! Allah U fane ka taelo ho masolomane ea hore le ka ‘na la tlola likano tsa lona tlas’a mabaka: ‘Allah ke Mos’ireletsi oa lona, U Tletse Tsebo, U Seli"
  66,3,"Ha Moprofeta a ne a phetela e mong oa basali ba hae taba lekunutung, eaba o phahlela e mong. Allah A etsa hore moporofeta a tsebe taba eo; eaba o lumellana le karolo e ngoe le hona ho hanana le karolo e ngoe ea taba eo. Joale, eitse ha a mo phetela, a re: “Ke mang ea o boleletseng taba ee?” Moporofeta a re: “Ke boleletsoe ke Ea tsebang tsohle, Ea hlokolosi ka ho fetisisa.”"
  66,4,"Ha le retelehela ho Allah ka boinyatso, lipelo tsa lona li lakatsa hoo; Empa haeba le ka ts’ietsana khahlano le eena, Ruri! Allah, ke Eena Mots’ireletsi oa hae, le Khabariele le ba lokileng har’a ba-kholoang; ho feta moo, manyeloi ke ba ts’ehetsi ba hae"
  66,5,"Haeba a ka le hlala, kamohlomong Allah U tla mo sitsa ka basali ba molemo ho le feta sebakeng, ba inehetseng, ba- kholoang, ba hlomphang Allah, ba retelehelang ho Allah ka boinyatso, ba khumamang ka boithapalatso, Ba hauhlaulang le ho ila, bahlolohali le ba es’o ang’oe ke monna"
  66,6,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Hlokomolohang mollo, lona le malapa a lona, oo libeseletso tsa ona e leng batho le majoe, o hlokometsoeng ke manyeloi a bohale, a tsitlaletseng, a bile a ke ke a latola taelo eo a e fuoang ke Allah, empa ba phethisa taelo"
  66,7,(Bat la re)“Lona Mahana-tumelo! Se keng la kopa ts’oarelo Kajeno. Le mpa le lefshoa ho latela tseo le neng le li etsa.”
  66,8,"Oho lona ba-kholoang! Retelehelang ho Allah ka boinyatso ba sebele! Ka ts’epo ea hore Mong`a lona U tla hlakola liketso tsohle tse mpe tsa lona le hona ho le amohela kahar’a Lirapa tseo linoka li phallang, –Letsatsi leo Allah A sa tl’ong ho phoqa Moporofeta le bohle ba kholoang le eena. Khanya ea bona e tlaba etella pele le ka matsohong a matona a bona ba tla be ba ts’oere litlaleho tsa bona: ba tla re: “Mong`a rona! Ak’u matlafatse khanya ea rona, U be U re ts’oarele! Hobane Ruri! Ke Uena Ea nang le matla holima lintho tsohle.”"
  66,9,"Oho Moporofeta! Tsitlalla ka thata khahlano le mahana- tumelo le Baikaketsi, u se be mosa ho bona. Lihele ke lehae la bona, – Pheletso e nyonyehang ruri"
  66,10,"Allah U fana ka papiso ho mahana-tumelo: Mosali oa Nooe le oa Lota, basali ba neng ba le tlas’a taolo ea makhabunyane a Rona a lokileng, le hoja ba ile ba ba eka, empa keko ea bona ha e ea ka ea ba thusa ka letho kapel’a Allah, lentsoe le ile la re ho bona: “Kenang Mollong ‘moho le bohle ba kenang.”"
  66,11,"Allah U fana ka papiso ho ba-kholoang: Mosali oa Faro: Bonang a re: “Mong`a ka! Ak’u nkahele ntlo ho pela Hau Serapeng, U be u ntopolle ho Faro le liketso tsa hae le ho ntopolla har’a batho ba etsang libe”"
  66,12,"Le Maria morali oa Imran, ea neng a hloekile. Eaba Re bolulela ka hare ho eena moea oa Rona. O ile a beha ts’epo mantsoeng a Mong`a hae le mangolong a Hae, e bile e mong oa ba hloekileng"
  67,1,Ea Hlohonolofetseng e be Eo Puso e leng Liatleng tsa Hae; Ea nang le Matla Oohle holima lintho tsohle
  67,2,"Eena Ea hlotseng Lefu le Bophelo, hore A tle A behe tekong mang le mango a lona ea boits’oaro bo nepahetseng. Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Ts’oarelang Khafetsa"
  67,3,"Eena Ea hlotseng maholimo a supileng ka tatelano: O tla bona tlholehong Ea Allah Ea Tletseng Lereko, kahoo sheba hape: O bona koli efe?”"
  67,4,"Talimisisa lekhetlo la bobeli: chalimo e tla boela ho uena e fifetse, e fokola, e khathetse"
  67,5,"Re khabisitse leholimo le ka tlase ka mabone, Re A entse likulo tse chalametsang ho leleka ea Mobe; Re ba hlophiselitse Kotlo ea Mollo o tukang"
  67,6,"Ba khesang Mong’a bona, ho teng Kotlo ea Lihele, e mpe pheletso"
  67,7,"Ha ba akheloa kahar’a ona, ba tla utloa mororo oa ona o ntse o tuka joalo"
  67,8,"O qhashoha ke khalefo. Nako le nako ha sehlopa se akheloa ka teng, ba lebeli ba ona ba tla botsa: “Ha ho ea ka ha fihla molemosi ho lona?”"
  67,9,"Ba tla re: “Ruri! Ho bile joalo, molemosi o ile a fihla ho rona; empa ra mo latola ka hore: “Allah ha A es’o ka a senola letho; u mpa u le phosong e ts’abehang.”"
  67,10,"Ba tla boela ba re: “Hoja re ile ra lemoseha kapa ra sebelisa kelello, Ruri! Re ka be re se har’a Balekane ba Khanare ea Mollo"
  67,11,"Joale bat la ipolela libe tsa bona, empa ts’oarelo e tla be e le hole le Balekane ba Khanare ea Mollo"
  67,12,"Haele ba ts’abang Mong’a bona ba sa ‘mone, ts’oarelo kea bona le moputso o moholo"
  67,13,"Ebang le pepesa lentsoe la lona kapa lea le pata, U na le tsebo e phethahetseng ea liphiri tsa lipelo tsohle"
  67,14,"Ha A ke ke A tseba-Eena Ea Hlotseng? Ke Eena Ea Utloisisang makunutu oohle, Ea Hlokolosi"
  67,15,"Ke Eena Ea hlotseng lefats’e ho nolofala, lebakeng la hau, kahoo tsamaea litseleng tsa lona, u je nala ea lona eo A u sitsitseng ka eona; Empa Tsoho e ho Eena"
  67,16,U ikutloa u sireletsehile hore Ea Maholimong A ke ke A etsa hore u metsoe ke lefats’e ha le reketla
  67,17,Kapa u ikutloa u sireletsehile hore Ea Maholimong A ke ke A romela Sefefo hore le tle le tsebe hore Temoso Ea Ka e joang
  67,18,"Empa ruri! batho pele ho bona ba latotse, joale e ile ea eba joang Tatolo Ea Ka"
  67,19,"Ha ba hlokomele linonyana kamoo li phukalatsang mapheo a tsona ka teng, li a khoale. Ha ho ope ea likakatletseng haese Ea TletsengLereko, Rurik e Eena Ea shebileng lintho tsohle"
  67,20,"Ke mang ea ka le thusang, le haele sesole, kantle ho Allah, Ea Tletseng Lereko? Mahana-tumelo ha ba ka har’a letho haese thetso"
  67,21,"Ke mang ea tlang ho le sitsa ka phepo, ha A ka khatla kabelo Ea Ha? Che, ba ngangaballa boikhohomosong le khelohong"
  67,22,"Ea tsamaeang a tiisitse hlooho, sefahleho sa hae se kebile, o tataisong e ntle,-Kapa ea tsamaeang ka makhethe Tseleng e Otlolohileng"
  67,23,"E re.” Ke Eena Ea le hlotseng, A sitsa ka kutlo, pono, boleng le kutloisiso: Empa teboho ea lona e ea fokola"
  67,24,"E re: “Ke eena ea le ngatafalitseng holim’a lefats’e, bohle le tla bokelloa ho Eena.”"
  67,25,"Ba ea botsa: “Ke neng ts’episo eo etlang ho phethahala haeba u bua ‘nete?”"
  67,26,"E re: “Tsebo ea nako e ho Allah A Inot’si, ‘Ke mpa ke le molemosi ea hlakileng.”"
  67,27,"Mohlang ba e bonelang hauts’oanyane, mahana-tumeloba ba tla sosobanya lifahleho, Ho tla thoe ho bona: “Sena ke seo le neng se bitsa.”"
  67,28,"E re: “Lea bona? Hore haeba Allah a ka ntimetsa hammoho le ba nang le ‘na, kapa A ts’ollela Mohau oa Hae holima rona, – joale ke mang ea tlang ho lopollaba Mahana-tumelo Kahlolong e mahlonoko?”"
  67,29,"E re: “U Tletse Lereko: Re kholoa ho Eena, re behile ts’epo ea rona ho Eena. Haufinyane le tla tseba hore na ke mang ea phosong e totobetseng.”"
  67,30,"E re: “Lea bona? – Haeba metsi oohle a lona a ka psha, ke mang ea ka etsang hore a kopotse lefats’eng"
  68,1,Nun. Ka pene le tlaleho e ngoloang
  68,2,Ka lereko la Mong`a hau ha u lehlanya
  68,3,Ruri! Moputso oa hau ke o sa feleng
  68,4,Tlholeho ea botho ba hau ke e babatsehang
  68,5,Haufi u tla bona le bona ba tla bona
  68,6,Hore na ke mang har’a lona ea hlanyango
  68,7,"Rurik e Mong’a hau Ea tsebang ka botlalo, ea khelohileng Tsela ea Hae: U tseba ka botlalo ba amohelang Tataiso"
  68,8,Kahoo se mamele bao ba latolang
  68,9,"Takatso ea bona ke hore u khelohe, hore ba tle ba khelohe"
  68,10,"Se natse mofuta oa motho ea nyonts’ang, – ea ikanang ka potlako"
  68,11,"Mofapanyi, ea tsamaeang a jala mashano"
  68,12,"Ea sitisang toka, ea tlolang meeli eohle, ea qoetseng sebeng"
  68,13,"Ea makoebeta, – ea silafetseng tlhahong"
  68,14,Hobane a sitsitsoe ka maruo le bara
  68,15,"Ha Lits’upiso tsa Rona li phetoa ho eena o re: “Lits’omo tsa mehleng ea khale.”"
  68,16,Haufi Re tla mo ts‘oea nko
  68,17,"Ruri! Re ba behile tekong joaloka ha Re ile Ra beha tekong Balekane ba Serapa, ha ba ne ba nka qeto ho khola litholoana e sa le hosasa"
  68,18,Empa ba se etse peheletso;(Ka Thato Ea Allah)
  68,19,"Eaba ho fihla moeti ho tsoa ho Mong’a hau, a hloekisa ba sa ile le sephume sa boroko"
  68,20,Kahoo Serapa hoseng sa tsoha eka sebaka se sets’o se shoeleng
  68,21,"Ha bosiu bo esa ba, ba bistsana ka bong’oe"
  68,22,“Eeang serapeng e sa le hosing ho khola litholoana.”
  68,23,"Ba tsamaea, ba hoeshetsa"
  68,24,“Le se lumelle mofutsana le ea mong ho kena ka har’a serapa kajeno
  68,25,"Ba qala letsatsi, ka qeto e khopameng"
  68,26,"Empa eitse ha ba bona serapa ba re: “Ruri! Re lahlehile"
  68,27,"Che, Re koaletsoe ka ntle"
  68,28,"E mong oa bona ea nang le toka a re: “Ha kea ka ka re ho lona le tlotlise Allah?”"
  68,29,"Ba re: “Tlotliso e be ho Mong’a rona! Ruri re ne re ntse re etsa bobe.”"
  68,30,"Ba fetohelana, ba qalella ho supana ka menoana, ba iphumana phoso"
  68,31,"Ba re: “Mehau ka rona! Re tlotse meeli e le ruri"
  68,32,“Mohlomong Mong`a rona U tla re neha se molemo ho feta sena. Hobane re retelehela ho Eena ka boinyatso.”
  68,33,"E joalo kahlolo. Empa e kholo kahlolo ea Bophelo Bo-tlang, – hoja ba ne ba tsebile"
  68,34,"Ruri! Sebakeng sa ba hloekileng ho teng lirapa tsa nyakallo, kapela Mong`a bona"
  68,35,Ana re ka ts’oara Batho-ba-Tumelo joalo ka Batho-ba-Sebe
  68,36,Molato ke eng ka lona? Le ahlola joang
  68,37,Kapa le na le Lengolo moo le ithutang teng
  68,38,Leo le tlang ho ba le tsohle tseo le ikhethelang tsona
  68,39,"Kapa le na le Selekane le Rona ka Kano, ho fihlela Letsatsi la Kahlolo, hore le tla fumana tsohle tseo le li batlang"
  68,40,Ak’u ba botse hore na ke mang har’a bona ea hlapanyang
  68,41,Kapa ba na le melingoana? Joale e re ba hlahise melingoana ea bona haeba ba buoa ‘nete
  68,42,"Letsatsi leo Tlhafu e tlang ho phetloa, e be ba ea bitsoa ho ithapalatsa ka lerato, Empa ba tla hloleha"
  68,43,"Mahlo a bona a tla be a talimile fats’e,-masoabi a ba aparetse; ha ba bona hore ba bilelitsoe pele-ho-nako ho tla ithapalatsa leratong, ba sa na le matla"
  68,44,"Ka hona ntese Ke Inots’i le bahanyetsi ba molaetsa ona: ka mekhahlelo Re tla lihela kotlo ho tsoa moo ba sa nahang"
  68,45,Ke tla ba ekeletsa nako. Ruri! Leano la Ka le Matla
  68,46,"Kapa u ba kopa moputso, kahoo ba tle ba imeloe ke moroalo oa sekoloto"
  68,47,"Kapa tse sa bonoeng li matleng a bona, hoo ba ka li ngolang fats’e"
  68,48,"Empa leta ka mamello taelo ea Mong`a hau, u se ke oa ts’oana le Molekane oa Tlhapi (Jonase) ha a ne a bokolla ke letsoalo"
  68,49,"Hoja Mohau oa Mong`a hae ha o oa ka oa mo fihlela, Ruri! A ka be a ile a lahleloa lebopong ka tlotlollo a tsotse"
  68,50,"Ka tsela eo Mong’a hae A mo khetha, A mo etsa e mong oa ba hloekileng"
  68,51,"Mahana-Tumelo ba ka batla ho ts’oasa ka mahlo ha ba utloa Moaletsa; ba re: Ruri ke lehlanya.”"
  68,52,"Empa ha se letho, haese molaetsa ho mafats’e ohle"
  69,1,‘Nete ea sebele
  69,2,‘Nete ea sebele ke eng
  69,3,Ke eng se tlang ho le hlokomelisa hore na ‘nete ea sebele ke eng
  69,4,Ba-Thamud le Ba-’Ad ba ile ba latola kotlo e tlang
  69,5,"Empa Ba-Thamud ba ile ba ripitloa ka sefefo sa lehalima le ‘mane, se ts`abehang"
  69,6,"Ba-`Ad, ba ripitliloe ka setsokotsane se bohale bo ts’abehang"
  69,7,"U ile A etsa hore se puputle masiu a supileng le matsatsi a robileng meno e ‘meli ka tatellano: kahoo u ka be u bone mofela oa batho ba tjapaletse, joaloka ha eka ke metso ea lifate tsa lipalema tse hlokang ‘moko li oele"
  69,8,Na u sa bona moneketsana feela oa bona
  69,9,"Le Faro, le ba bileng teng pele ho eena, le metse-moholo e repitliloeng, ka lebaka la Sebe"
  69,10,"Ba se mamele moromuoa oa Mong`a bona, kahoo A ba neha kotlo e matla"
  69,11,Re ile Ra u jara ka Areka mohlang metsi a neng a roaletse
  69,12,"Hore Re etse molaetsa ho uena, hore litsebe li-utloe, kelello e hopole"
  69,13,"Joale, mohla Terompeta e letsoang hang"
  69,14,"Lefats’e le tsitsingoang le lithaba tsa lona, li fetohang lerole hang, –"
  69,15,"Letsatsing leo, ketsehalo e tla phethahala"
  69,16,"Leholimo le tla aroha ka lehare, hobane letsatsing leo le tla be le fokola"
  69,17,"Manyeloi a tla be a le mahlakoreng a lona, a robeli a jarile terone ea Mong`a ka holim’a ona"
  69,18,"Letsatsing leo le tla biletsoa kahlolong, ha ho ketso le e ng`oe ea hau eo u e patang, e tlang ho pateha"
  69,19,"Joale ea tla nehoa tlaleho ea hae ka letsohong la molema, o tla re: “Nka, ba la tlaleho ea ka"
  69,20,“Ruri ke ile ka utloisisa hore tlaleho ea ka e tla mphihlela!”
  69,21,"Joale, o tla ba bophelong ba khotso"
  69,22,Serapeng se phahameng
  69,23,"Seo litholoana li leng haufi, li fihleleha"
  69,24,"“Ejang le noe, ka khotsofalo; ka lebaka la tseo le lirometseng nale, matsatsing a fetileng"
  69,25,"Ea tlang ho nehoa tlaleho ea hae letsohong la ntsohohlo, o tla re: “Jonna! Hoja ka se ke ka nehoa tlaleho ea ka"
  69,26,“Le hona ho hlokomela hore na tlaleho ea ka e eme joang
  69,27,“Hoja lefu ha lea ka la ntsometsa
  69,28,“Leruo la ka ha lena thuso ho `na
  69,29,“Matla a ka a felile!”
  69,30,"(Taelo e tla re)“Mo ts’oare, le mo tlame"
  69,31,“Le mochese Khanareng ea Mollo
  69,32,"“Le mo-khoantise a tlang`oe ka ketane, e bolele ba limitara tse mashome a supileng"
  69,33,“Enoa kea neng a sa kholoe ho Allah Ea Matla Oohle
  69,34,“A sa khothaletse phepo ea mafutsana
  69,35,“Kahoo ha ana motsoalle kajeno
  69,36,"“Kapa tsona lijo, ntle le ts’ila e hlatsoitseng maqeba"
  69,37,“E sa jeoeng ke ope haese baetsalibe.”
  69,38,“Ke le biletsa bopaking ka tseo le li bonang”
  69,39,“Le tseo le sa li boneng
  69,40,“Hore Ruri lena ke lentsoe la morumuoa ea hlomphehang
  69,41,"“Ha se lentsoe seroki: le kholoa hanyane"
  69,42,"“Kapa lona lentsoe la senohe: khalemo eo le e fumanang ke e fokolang"
  69,43,“Molaetsa o rometsoeng ho tsoa ho Mong`a Mafats’e
  69,44,“Haeba morumuoa u ne a ka iqapela lipuo Ka lebitso la Rona
  69,45,Ruri re tla moshakarela ka letsoho la hae la molema
  69,46,Ruri Re tla mo khaola mothapo oa pelo
  69,47,Ha ho mang oa lona ea ka mo sireletsang
  69,48,Empa ruri! Sena ke Molaetsa ho ts’abang Allah
  69,49,Re’a tseba hore har’a lona ho na le ba o hanyetsang
  69,50,Empa ruri Ke sehlabi ho Mahana-tumelo
  69,51,Empa ruri ke ‘Nete ea sebele
  69,52,"Kahoo, tlotlisang lebitso la Mong`a lona Ea Matla Oohle"
  70,1,Motsi o botsitse ka Kotlo e tlang ho oela
  70,2,"Mahana-tumelo, eo ho seng ea ka e qobang"
  70,3,E tsoang ho Allah Mong`a Litsela tsa Nyolohelo
  70,4,Tseo manyeloi le Khabariele a nyolohelang ho Eena ka letsatsi leo tekanyo ea lona e ka bang likete tse mashome a mahlano a lilemo
  70,5,"U mamelle, – ka Mamello e hlokang khoao"
  70,6,Ruri! Letsatsi ba le bonela thoko haholo
  70,7,Empa Re le bonela haufinyane
  70,8,Letsatsi leo ka lona leholimo le tlang ho ho ba joalo ka lesheleshele la koporo
  70,9,Lithaba li tla ts’oana le boea
  70,10,Ha ho motsoalle ea tla botsa ka motsoalle oa hae
  70,11,Le hoja ba tla be ba filoe pono ea hore ba bonane. Takatso ea moetsalibe; e tla ba e ka a ka itokolla Kahlolong ea Letsatsi leo ka ho itefella ka bana ba hae
  70,12,Ka mosali oa hae le ka ngoana’bo
  70,13,Kapa ka beng ka eena ba mo holisitseng
  70,14,"Le ka bohle ba teng mona lefats’eng, haeba ho khoneha ho mo lopolla"
  70,15,Empa che! Ruri! E tla be e le Mollo oa Lihele
  70,16,Khanare e qaqapollang lehata
  70,17,"E memang bohle ba khelohileng, ba furalla"
  70,18,Ba bokella maruo ba a khoaela
  70,19,Ruri! Motho o bopiloe a hloka mamello
  70,20,A phakisa a khopeha ha bomalimabe bo mo fihlela
  70,21,"Empa ha lehlohonolo le mo fihlela, oba leqe ka lona"
  70,22,Kantle le barapeli
  70,23,Ba tsitlaletseng thapelong ea bona
  70,24,Bao thepeng ea bona ho nang le litokelo tse fanoeng
  70,25,Malebana le mafutsana a kopang le ea hlolehang
  70,26,Ba kakatletseng ‘neteng ea Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  70,27,Ba ts’abang mesarelo ea Mong`a bona –
  70,28,Hobane Mesarelo ea Mong`a bona e khahlanong le Khotso le Boiketlo; –
  70,29,Ba bolokileng bohloeki ba bona
  70,30,"Kantle le basali ba bona le bao matsoho a matona a bona a ba ruileng, kahoo ba ke keba behoa molato"
  70,31,"Empa haele ba tlolang meeli eo, Ruri! bao e tla be e le batloli ba melao"
  70,32,Ka ho ts’oana le ba bolokang likano tsa bona le selekane sa bona
  70,33,Le ba its’etlehileng ka bopaki ba bona
  70,34,Hammoho le bohle ba hlokolosi lithapelong tsa bona
  70,35,Ruri! bana ba tla phela kahar’a Lirapa tse hlomphehang
  70,36,Molato ke eng ka mahana-tumelo haele moo ba u tonetse mahlo
  70,37,Ka lehlakoreng le letona le le lets’eali ka mekhahlelo
  70,38,Ana motho e mong le e mong har’a bona o rata ho kena kahar’a Serapa sa Nyakallo
  70,39,"Che, Ruri! Re ba hlotse ka seo ba se tsebang"
  70,40,Ke ikana ka Mong`a ‘nqa tsohle tsa Bochabela le Bophirima hore re na le matla
  70,41,Ho beha ba betere ho ba feta sebakeng sa bona. Re ke ke ra hloloa
  70,42,"Kahoo, ba tlohele ho itaola le ho bapala ho fihlela ba kopana le letsatsi la bona leo ba le ts’episitsoeng"
  70,43,Eleng letsatsi leo ba tlang ho tsosoa mabitleng ka potlako joaloka ha eka ke litlholisano ho ea leseleng
  70,44,"Ka mahlo a ts’ohileng, ba bile ba aparetsoe ke masoabi: leo e tla be ele letsatsi leo ba le ts’episitsoeng"
  71,1,"Ruri! Re ile Ra romella Nooe ho batho ba habo: “Lemosa batho ba heno esere kahlolo e mahlonoko ea tloha ea ba oela holimo"
  71,2,"A re: “Oho batho ba heso! Ruri! Ke mohlokomelisi ea totobetseng ho lona"
  71,3,"“Hore le tlameha ho khumamela Allah le hona ho mo sebeletsa ka tieo, le nkutloe"
  71,4,"“Hore A tle A le ts’oarele libe tsa lona le hona ho lelefatsa nako ea lona ea pallo. Hobane Ruri! Nako eo pallo ea Allah e tlang, e ke ke ea liehisoa hoja le ne le tseba.”"
  71,5,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! Ke ne ke etsa pitso ho batho ba heso bosiu le mots’eare"
  71,6,Empa lipitso tsohle tsa ka ha li’a ka tsa thusa letho haese hona hore ba balehe ‘neteng
  71,7,"“Hobane ka linako tsohle ha ke ba bitsetsa hore U tle U ba ts’oarele, ba kiba litsebe tsa bona ka menoana le hona ho ipata lifahleho ka liaparo tsa bona; ba tsitlaletse nyefolong le hona ho ikhohomosa"
  71,8,“Ke ba hoelelitse ka lentsoe le phahameng
  71,9,“Ke ile ka phatlalatsa molaetsa pooaneng ho bona; ka etsa kopo ho bona sephiring
  71,10,"“Ke re: kopang ts’oarelo ho Mong`a lona. Hobane U Ts’oarela ka Mehla eohle"
  71,11,“Etsoe U tla le nesetsa lipula tsa litloebelele
  71,12,“A le ekeletse maruo le bara; A le sitse ka Lirapa le Linoka tse phallang
  71,13,“Molato ke eng ka lona haele moo le hloka ts’epo ho Allah molemong oa boits’oaro bo nepahetseng
  71,14,Empa e le Eena Ea le hlotseng ka mekhahlelo e fapaneng
  71,15,Na ha le bone kamoo Allah a hlotseng maholimo a supileng kateng ka tatellano
  71,16,A tsepamisa ngoeli ho ba khanya leholimong le lona letsatsi ho ba lebone
  71,17,“Ke Allah ea le hlahisitseng leroleng la lefats’e
  71,18,"“Pheletsong U tla boela A le busetsa ho lona hape, U tla le tsosa hape ka Letsatsi la Tsoho"
  71,19,“Allah U le aletse lefats’e
  71,20,“Hore le tle le hahlaule holim’a lona ka litsela tse pharaletseng.”
  71,21,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! ba ntatotse, eaba ba sala morao batho bao thepa le bana ba bona li sa tl’ong ho ba thusa ka letho haese Tahleho"
  71,22,“Ba lohile leqheka le ts’abehang
  71,23,"“Ba re: “Le se lahle melingoana ea lona kherehloa. E leng Wadd kapa Suw’a, le haele Yaghuth, Ya’uq kapa Nasr"
  71,24,"Ruri! Ba khelositse batho ba bangata tseleng, uena ha ho kamoo u ka putsang baetsalibe kateng haese ka ho kheloha.”"
  71,25,"Ba ile ba khamisoa metsi ho latela libe tsa bona, eaba ba akheloa Mollong. Ha ho bathusi ba ileng ba ba fumana ntle ho Allah"
  71,26,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! U se siee leha e le moneketsela feela oa moetsalibe lefats’eng"
  71,27,"Hobane haeba U ka ba siea, ba tla khelosa makhabunyane a Hau le tsoala tsa bona e tla ba baetsalibe"
  71,28,"Mong`a ka! U nts’oarele ‘moho le batsoali ba ka le ba-kholoang bohle ba keneng lelapeng la ka, banna le basali, U se ke oa putsa baetsalibe ka letho haese timelo"
  72,1,"E re: “Ke senoletsoe hore sehlopha sa Li-jinn li ne li thehile tsebe ho mamela[Qur`an], tsa re: “Re fela re utloile palo e babatsehang"
  72,2,"“E tataisetsa tokeng, re khotsoe ka hona: ha re na ho kopanya mong le mong le Mong`a rona"
  72,3,"“Bo phahame Botlotlehi ba Mong`a rona: ha A na molekane kapa mora"
  72,4,"“Ho ne ho ena le maoatla har’a rona, ba neng ba tloaetse ho buoa mashano a matala ka Allah"
  72,5,“Empa rea lumela hore motho kapa moea ha ba na tokelo ea ho bua leshano ka Allah
  72,6,"“Ruri! Ho teng batho, ba batlang ts’ireletso ho Li-Jinn, empa li ba ekelelitse phosong"
  72,7,"“Ba nahana joaloka uena, hore Allah ha ana ho tsosa ope bafung –"
  72,8,“Re ile ra leka ho phahlolla makunutu a leholimo; empa ra fumana le lebetsoe ke balebeli ba matla le malakabe a mollo
  72,9,"“Re ne re lula re larile, ho utsoa; empa ke mong le mong ea neng a leka ho mamela u iphumana a lelekoa ke lelakabe le chalametsang"
  72,10,"“Ha re utloisisi hore na kotlo e lebisitsoe ho boohle lefats’eng, kapana Mong`abona Urerilehobatataisatselengnepahetseng"
  72,11,"“Ho na le ba bang hara rona ba lokileng, ba bang ba fapane: re latela litsela tse fapaneng"
  72,12,"“Empa re’a tseba hore re ke ke ra ferekanya merero ea Allah, kapa hona ho Mo ferekanya ka paleho"
  72,13,"“Haele rona, re utloang tataiso, re amohetse mang le mang ea kholoang ho `Mopi oa hae ha ana ts`abo, ea qhekanyetso kapa bohanyapetsi"
  72,14,"“Hara rona ho na le ba ithobelang Allah, le ba tsoang tseleng ea toka. – haele ba ithobileng –ba nkile tsela e topileng"
  72,15,"“Empa haele ba tsoapohang, ke libeso tsa Mollo-oa-Lihele"
  72,16,"“Haeba ba ile ba tsitlallela tseleng, Re ka be Re ba sitisitse ka pula tsa matlopotlopo"
  72,17,"“E le hore Re ba behe tekong. Empa mong le mong ea tla kheloha khopolong ea Mong`a hae, U tla mo otla ka kotlo e mahlonoko"
  72,18,"“Libaka tsa thapelo ke tsa Allah: kahoo le se bitse ho mong kantle ho Allah"
  72,19,"“Nakong eo lekhabunyane la Allah le emang ho Mo rapela, ba mo opela hare ka bongata"
  72,20,"E re: “Ke rapela Allah a Inotsi, ha ke Mo kopanye le mang kapa mang.”"
  72,21,"E re: “Ha ke na matla a ho le utloisa bohloko, kapa hona ho le tlisa tseleng e nepahetseng.”"
  72,22,"E re: “Ha ho ea ka nts’ireletsang khahlanong le Allah, kapa ho fumana sets’abelo kantle ho Eena,”"
  72,23,"“Mosebetsi oa ka ke ho phatlalatsa seo ke se fumanang ho tsoa ho Allah, ho phtlalatsa molaetsa oa Hae. Haele ba nyefolang Allah le moromuoa oa Hae: ba loketsoe ke lihele, ba tla phela moo kahosafeleng”"
  72,24,"Khabareng, ha ba bona tseo ba neng ba li ts’epistoe, – ka nako eo ba tla tseba hore na ke mang ea fokolang e le mothusi, ea eisehang ka lipalo"
  72,25,"E re: Ha ke tsebe hore na seo le neng le se ts’episitsoe se haufi, kapa Mong`a ka U hlophisitse nako e telele ea pallo malebana le eona"
  72,26,"Hobane ke Eena Ea tsebang tse sa bonoeng; ebile ha ho mang, kapa mang eo A mo senolelang sephiri sa Hae"
  72,27,"Haese ho moromuoa ofe, kapa ofe eo a khahloang ke Eena, joale ebe U hlomamisa balebeli (manyeloi) ho tsamaea kapel’a hae le kamor’a hae"
  72,28,"Hore a tle a tsebe hore e feela ba phatlalalitse melaetsa ea Mong`a bona. U bile U kopetse hare liketso tsohle tseo ba li etsang, U boloka tlaleho ea lintho tsohle"
  73,1,Oho uena ea its`opileng ka seaparo
  73,2,"Ema bosiu, empa e seng bosiu boohle"
  73,3,"Karolo ea bona, kapa ka tlase ho moo"
  73,4,"Kapa haholoanyane, o phete Qur`an ka tekanyo ea lentsoe butle"
  73,5,Haufi Re tla romela molaetsa oa bohlokoa ho uena
  73,6,"Ruri! Ho tsoha bosiu ho bohlokoa molemong oa taolo ea phefomoloho ea hau, e molemo haholo sebakeng sa Lentsoe"
  73,7,Ruri! Mots’eare le na le mesebetsi eo le e etsang
  73,8,Empa tsitlallela khopolong ea lebitso la Mong`a hau; ikitlaelletsa ho Eena ka pelo eohle
  73,9,"Mong`a Bochabela le Bophirima: ha ho `Mopi kantle ho Eena; ikhethele Eena feela e le mosireletsi oa hau"
  73,10,"U be le mamello ho seo ba se buang, o tlohe pela bona ka tlhompho"
  73,11,"U ntese ho sebetsana le ba nang le lintho tse khotsofatsang tsa lefats`e, ba latolang `nete; u ba nehe nyehlisetso ha nakoana"
  73,12,Re na le mahlahlela a boima le mollo o chesang
  73,13,"Le lijo tse khamang, le kotlo e mahlonoko"
  73,14,Ka Letsatsi le leng lefats’e le lithaba li tla tsukutleha. Le lithaba li tla fetoha qubu ea lehlabathe le qhalanang
  73,15,"Re le romeletse, moromuoa, eo e tla ba paki khahlano le lona, joalo ka ha Re ile Ra romella moromuoa ho Faro"
  73,16,"Empa Faro o ile a latola moromuoa, Re ile Ra mo nanola ka kotlo e boima"
  73,17,"Joale ha o latola Allah, o tla its’ireletsa joang ka letsatsi leo Bana ba tlang ho ba moriri o moputsoa"
  73,18,Mohlang leholimo le patsohang ka lehare? Ts’episo ea Hae e tla phethahala
  73,19,"Ruri! Sena ke keletso: kahoo, ea ratang, a nke tsela e eang ho Mong`a hae"
  73,20,"Mong`a hau U oa tseba hore o ne o ema karolo-bobeli e boraro ea bosiu, kapa karolo ea bosiu, kapa karolo ng`oe ea boraro, le ka ho ts`oana le karolo eaba nang uena. Empa Allah U lekanya bosiu le mots’eare, hore u tsebe ho boloka palo moo. Kahoo u retelehetse ka ho uena ka mohau: bala, likarolo tsa Qur`an ka mokhoa oo le ka etsang tse bonolo. U tsebe ka botlalo hore ho ka `na haeba ba fokolang bophelong hara lona; ba bang ke bahahlauli, ba tsomana le nala ea Allah, ha ba bang ba loana tseleng ea Allah, bala Qur`an ka mokhoa oo le ka khonang; le rapele kamehla, le fane ka nyehelo; le alime Allah, kalimo e ntle. Etsoe botle bohle boo le bo romelang nale sebakeng sa phefomoloho ea lona le tla bo fumana kapela Allah; Eea, bo phahame ka moputso, le batle Lereko la Allah; Allah U Ts’oarela-khafetsa, U Mohau o Khaphatsehang"
  74,1,Oho uena ea ikhatlileng
  74,2,Tsoha u fane ka temoso
  74,3,U rorise Mong`a hau
  74,4,Liaparo tsa hau u li hloekise
  74,5,U nene tsohle tse mpe
  74,6,"Kapa phanong ea hau, oa labella kuno"
  74,7,"Empa u be le mamello, u tsitlalle tseleng ea Mong`a hau"
  74,8,"Qetellong, ha Terompeta e lla"
  74,9,Leo e tlaba Letsatsi; Letsatsi la mahlomola
  74,10,Le seng bonolo ho ba se nang tumelo
  74,11,"Ntese, le eo ke mo hlotseng Ke Inots’i"
  74,12,Eo Ke mo sitsitseng ka melemo e fetang tekano
  74,13,Le bara ho ba pela hae
  74,14,Eo ke mo nolofalelitseng bophelo
  74,15,Empa o meharo hore ke mo ekeletse
  74,16,"Che, ho lits`opiso tsa Rona o khopame"
  74,17,Haufinyane Ke tla mo lahlela Mollong-oa-Lihele
  74,18,"U nahanne, a loha maqiti; –"
  74,19,Sekhobo se be ho eena; kamoo a lohileng maqiti
  74,20,"Ee, sekhobo se be ho eena; kamoo a lohileng maqiti! –"
  74,21,Eaba o oa qamaka
  74,22,"Eaba o busa lifahleho, o oa koata"
  74,23,Eaba o furalla ka boikhants’o
  74,24,"Eaba o re: “Sena ha se letho haese boloi, ba mehleng ea khale"
  74,25,Sena ke lentsoe la motho.”
  74,26,Hahufinyane! Ke tla mo lahlela Mollong oa Lihele
  74,27,Ke`ng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na Mollo-oa-Lihele ke eng
  74,28,"Ha o lumelle letho ho phela, le hona ho tlohela feela! –"
  74,29,O nts`ofatsa le ho fetola `mala oa motho
  74,30,Holima ona hona le ba leshome le metso e robong
  74,31,"Ha ho ope ntle le manyeloi joalo ka ba hlokomeli ba mollo; palo e tsepamisitsoeng e le teko ho mahana-tumelo, – hore batho ba Lengolo ba tle ba fihlele qeto, le ba-kholoang ba eketse ho tiisa tumelong; – ba nang le khoao ba tlohetse Batho- ba-Lengolo le ba-kholoang, le bao pelong tsa bona ho nang le maloetse le mahana-tumelo ba ka`na ba re: “E be Allah U bolelang ka papiso ee?” Allah U khelosa ea ratoang ke Eena, U tataisa ea ratoang ke Eena: ha ho ea ka tsebang ka matla a Mong`a hau, kantle ho Eena. Sena ke molaetsa ho batho"
  74,32,"Che, Ruri; ka ngoeli"
  74,33,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  74,34,Le ka meso ha mafube a hlaha
  74,35,Sena empa e le se seng sa lits’upiso tse kholohali
  74,36,Temoso ho batho
  74,37,Ho e mong le e mong oa lona ea khethang tsela e nepahetseng
  74,38,Phefomoloho ka ngoe e tla paka liketso tsa eona
  74,39,Kantle le balekane ba letsoho la molema
  74,40,"Lirapeng: ba tla botsana"
  74,41,Ba botse baetsalibe
  74,42,“Ke eng se le isitseng Mollong-oa-Lihele?”
  74,43,"Ba tla re: “Re bile sieo ho ba neng ba rapela”"
  74,44,“Kapa ba neng ba fepa mafutsana
  74,45,“Re ne re le mokhatlong oa basomi
  74,46,“Re ne re latola Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  74,47,“Ho fihlela lefu le re oela holimo.”
  74,48,Ha ho na ‘muelli ea tla bang molemo ho bona
  74,49,Joale molato ke eng ka bona hobane ba ile ba furalla temoso
  74,50,Joaloka ha eka ke lipokola li ts’ohile
  74,51,Li baleha tau
  74,52,"Mehlolo, mong le mong o batla ho fuoa maqhepe a manolotsoeng"
  74,53,"Che, ha ba na letsoalo la Bo-tlang"
  74,54,"Che, Ruri sena ke temoso"
  74,55,Mong le mong ea nang le hona a inkele temoso
  74,56,"Empa ha ho mong ea tla e boloka ka khopolo, kantle ho thato ea Allah: ke Mong`a Botlehali, le tsoarelo"
  75,1,Ka Letsatsi la Tsoho (ea bafu)
  75,2,Le ka phefomoloho e tletseng boinyatso
  75,3,Motho ha a hopole hore Re ka kopanya masapo a hae
  75,4,"Che, Re na le matla a ho kopanya menoana ea hae ka tatellano"
  75,5,Empa motho o lakatsa ho etsa bobe ka nako e ka pela hae
  75,6,"O a botsa: “Letsatsi la tsoho le neng?”"
  75,7,"Khabareng, mohla pono e fifalang"
  75,8,Ngoeli li fifalang
  75,9,Letsatsi le ngoeli li kopangoang
  75,10,"Ke letsatsi leo motho a tla re: “Sets`abelo sa ka se ho kae?”"
  75,11,Che! Ha hona sets’abelo
  75,12,"Kapela Mong`a hau, letsatsing leo e tla ba sebaka sa phomolo"
  75,13,"Letsatsing le motho o tla bolelloa pale ea hae, le tsohle tse a li siileng morao"
  75,14,"Che, motho o tla paka khahlano le eena"
  75,15,Leha a ka leka ho its`ereletsa
  75,16,U se bule molomo oa hau u potlaketse qeto
  75,17,Ho ho Rona ho bona pokello ea eona le phatlalatso
  75,18,"Ha Re se Re e phatlalalitse, e latele"
  75,19,Ho ho Rona ho e hlalosa
  75,20,"Che, empa motho a rata bophelo bo fetang hang"
  75,21,A tlohela bophelo Bo-tlang
  75,22,"Letsatsing leo, lifahleho tse ling li tla be li khanya"
  75,23,Li talimme ho Mong`a tsona
  75,24,"Ha tse ling, letsatsing leo, li tla be lihloname, li soabile"
  75,25,Ka khopolo ea hore bomalimabe boo mahlonoko bo tlilo liheloa holima tsona
  75,26,"Ruri, ha phefomoloho e fihla ‘metsong"
  75,27,"Hoba le mohoo, “Ke mang moloi?”"
  75,28,O tla qeta hore ke nako ea karohano
  75,29,Leoto le tla kopang`oa le le leng
  75,30,Mohlang oo tsela tsohle lit la lebisa ho Mong`a hau
  75,31,"Ha a nyehela letho, le hona ho rapela"
  75,32,Empa o latotse `nete. A furalla
  75,33,A hoantela ho mehahabo ka boikhants’o bohle
  75,34,"Sekhobo se be ho uena, ee, sekhobo"
  75,35,"Hape sekhobo se be ho uena, ee, sekhobo"
  75,36,Motho o hopola hore o tla siuoa a sa laoloe
  75,37,Ene e se lerotholi la there e thakhintsoeng
  75,38,Eaba o fetoha lehloele; eaba Allah U `mopa ho mo neha sebopeho
  75,39,"A `mopa ka bobeli, monna le mosali"
  75,40,Ha se Eena A nang le matla a ho phelisa bafu
  76,1,Ho ne ho se motsotso oo motho e ne e se letho le ka hopoloang
  76,2,"Ruri! Re hlotse motho ka lerotholi la tere, e le ho ‘meha tekong: Ra mo neha kutlo le pono"
  76,3,Ra mo bonts’a tsela; hore a lebohe kapa a hloke teboho
  76,4,"Mahana-tumelo Re a hlophiselitse liketane, lijoko le Mollo"
  76,5,"Ba lokileng, ba tla noella mopotjoaneng, o kopantsoeng le kafur"
  76,6,"Selibeng seo makhabunyane a Allah a noang ho sona, se ts’akhunyang ka matlopotlopo"
  76,7,"Ba phethisa likano, ba ts`aba letsatsi leo bobe ba lona bo tlang ho jaleha ka bophara"
  76,8,"Ba fepa mafutsana, likhutsana, le ba ts’oaruoa, leratong la Allah"
  76,9,"[ba re] “Re le fepa ka lereko la Allah Ea Inots`i: Ha re`a lebella moputso kapa tsona liteboho ho lona"
  76,10,Re ts’aba letsatsi leo ka lona khalefo ea Mong`a rona e tla beng e tlokoma.”
  76,11,"Empa Allah u tla ba lopolla bomalimabeng ba letsatsi leo, A ba khants`etse ka botle le nyakallo"
  76,12,"Hobane ba ne ba ena le mamello ba tsitlalletse, u tla ba putsa ka serapa le silika"
  76,13,"Ba tla phomola Literoneng tse phahameng, ba ke ke ba bona mocheso oa letsatsi kapa serame se hlabang"
  76,14,"Meriti e tlaba haufi le bona, liririella tsa litholoana li tla atamela pela bona ka ho ithoba"
  76,15,Har’a bona ho tla feta lijana tsa silivera le mepotjoana ea krystal
  76,16,"Tse khanyang sa khalase, tse entsoeng ka silivera: li tla lekanya litabatabelo tsa bona"
  76,17,Ba tla nehoa mopotjoana o kopantsoeng le zanjabil
  76,18,Seliba se bitsoang Salsabil
  76,19,"Ba tla feptjoa ke morolo o mosesane o sa tsofaleng; ha u ba bona, u tla nahana hore ke liperela tse qhalaneng"
  76,20,"E tla re ha u sheba, ke moo o tlang, ho bona khotso le sebaka se botlehali"
  76,21,"Ba tla be ba apere liaparo tse tala tsa silika le brocade, ba roetse lipetja tsa silivera; Mong`a bona U ba neha veine e hloekileng e halalelang ho noa"
  76,22,"“Ruri! Sena ke moputso oa lona, le ts`ebetso ea lona e amohetsoe.”"
  76,23,Ke rona ba rometseng Qur`an ho lona ka mekhahleho
  76,24,Kahoo ebang le mamello ka tsitlallelo ho taelo ea Mong`a lona le se mamele baetsalibe le banyefoli har`a bona
  76,25,Tlotlisa lebitso la Mong`a hau hoseng le mantsiboea
  76,26,"Le karolong ea bosiu, Mo khumamele, u Mo tlotlise bosiu bohle"
  76,27,"Haele bana, ba rata bophelo ba lepotla-potla, ba itebatsa letsatsi le mahlonoko"
  76,28,"Ke Rona ba ba hlotseng, Ra matlafatsa linoka tsa bona; empa, ha Re rata, Re ka ba fapanyetsana ka ba bang ba ts’oanang le bona"
  76,29,"Sena ke temoso: ea ratang, a inkele tsela e eang ho Mong`a hae"
  76,30,"Empa ha u ke ke, kantle ho thato ea Allah: hobane Allah U na le tsebo e phahametseng, U Seli"
  76,31,"U tla amohela mohaung oa Hae ea ratoang ke eena; empa baetsalibe, – U ba hlophiselitse kahlolo e mahlonoko"
  77,1,Ka liphefo tse romelloang ka tatellano
  77,2,Tse foqohang ka matla
  77,3,Lijala hole le haufi
  77,4,Li arole se seng ho se seng
  77,5,Li phatlalatse molaetsa hoohle
  77,6,Oa topollo kapa oa temoso
  77,7,Ruri! Seo le se ts’episitsoeng se tla phethahala
  77,8,Mohla linaleli li fifalang
  77,9,Leholimo le petsoha ka lehare
  77,10,Lithaba li qhalahangoa se ka lerole
  77,11,Le baromuoa ba khobokang’oang pallong ea bona –
  77,12,Ke letsatsi lefe la tsee tse boleloang
  77,13,Ke tsa Letsatsi la Tlhopho
  77,14,Ke`ng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na letsatsi la tharollo ke eng! –
  77,15,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,16,Ha Re ea ka Ra ripitlila meloko ea mathomo
  77,17,Le ka e latelang ho moo Re tla etsa joalo
  77,18,Re sebetsa joalo ka baetsalibe
  77,19,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,20,Ha Re’a u hlola ka lero le eisehang
  77,21,Ra le beha sebakeng sa phomolo ka tsepamo
  77,22,Ka nako e baliloeng
  77,23,Hobane Re ea hlopha; Re hlopha ka pabatseho
  77,24,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,25,Ha Re ea hlola lefats’e ho ba tulo
  77,26,Ho tse phelang le tse shoeleng
  77,27,"Ra hlola lithaba ho tsepama, tse phahameng; Ra le sitsa ka metsi a hlabosang"
  77,28,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,29,"[ho tla thoe] “Tlohang mona ho seo le neng se latola ka ho se shanofatsa"
  77,30,“E eang moriting o menahaneng ha raro
  77,31,"“Oo ho senang ho phola, o se nang thuso lebataneng la mocheso"
  77,32,“Ruri! O tlola mollo e le qhobosheane
  77,33,“Joaloka ha eka ke likamele tse ts’ehla.”
  77,34,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,35,Ke letsatsi leo ho senang ea tla beng a tseba ho buoa
  77,36,Kapa ho lumelloa ho ipuella
  77,37,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,38,Leo e tla be e le letsatsi la tlhopho! Re tla le khobokanya ‘moho le meloko e tlileng pele ho lona
  77,39,"Joale, haeba le na le leqheka, nqhekanyetseng"
  77,40,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,41,"Haele ba lokileng, ba tlaba tlasa moriti le pela liliba"
  77,42,"Le litholoana, – sohle seo ba se labalabelang"
  77,43,"“E jang le noe le khotsofale: seo le se sebelelitseng.”"
  77,44,Ke kamoo Re putsang ba etsi ba tse ntle kateng
  77,45,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ’nete letsatsing leo
  77,46,Ejang le nyakalle ha nakoana. Ruri! Leba etsalibe
  77,47,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba ‘nete letsatsing leo
  77,48,"Ha ho thoe ho bona: “Khumamang!” Ha ba etse joalo"
  77,49,Sekhobo se be ho balatoli ba nnete letsatsing leo
  77,50,"Ke molaetsa ofe ka morao ho moo, ba tlang ho o kholoa"
  78,1,Ba hanyetsana ka eng
  78,2,Ka litaba tse molemo
  78,3,Tseo ba ke keng ba lumellana ka tsona
  78,4,"Ruri, haufi ba tla ruoa tsebo"
  78,5,Ruri! Ruri haufi ba tla ruoa tsebo
  78,6,Ha Re ea pharalatsa lefats’e
  78,7,Ra tsepamisa lithaba
  78,8,Re le hlotse ka bobeli
  78,9,Ra hlophisa boroko ho ba phomolo ea lona
  78,10,Ra hlophisa bosiu ho ba sekhurumetso
  78,11,Le mots’ehare hore e be molemong oa lona
  78,12,Ra aha maholimo a supileng kaholim’a lona
  78,13,Ra beha teng khanya e babatsehang
  78,14,Re ts’ollella lipula tsa melupe ho tsoa marung
  78,15,Re melisang lijothollo le meroho
  78,16,Le lirapa tsa makhasi a lipapetloa
  78,17,Ruri! Letsatsi la tharollo ke nako ea pallo
  78,18,Letsatsi leo ka lona Terompeta e tla letsoa; le tla phalla ka likete-kete
  78,19,Le leholimo le tla phetloa joalo ka ha e ka ho na le likhoro
  78,20,Lithaba li tla nyamela joalo ka mohuli
  78,21,Ruri! Lihele ke sebaka sa khaoletsi
  78,22,Lehae la baetsalibe
  78,23,Mooba tlang ho phela teng mengoaha
  78,24,"Moo ba ke keng ba latsoa letho le pholileng, kapa seno"
  78,25,"Kantle ho mokelikeli o belang, mokelikeli o mots’o, o nkhang, o serame se qhoalisang"
  78,26,Ele moputso o ba ts`oanetseng
  78,27,Hobane! ba ne ba sa ts`abe qoso
  78,28,Empa ba latola lits’upiso tsa rona ba re ke leshano
  78,29,Tsohle li ngoliloe bukeng ea tlaleho
  78,30,"Kahoo, latsoang litholoana tsa mesebetsi ea lona; ha ho kekeletso eo le tlang ho e nehoa, ntle le kahlolo.”"
  78,31,Ruri! Ho ba lokileng ho teng phethiso ea litabatabelo tsa bona –
  78,32,Lirapa tsa merara
  78,33,Le baroetsana ba es’ong ho amane le banna
  78,34,Le mepotjoana e khaphatsehang
  78,35,Kamoo ba ke keng ba utloa lipuo tsa mafeela le leshano; –
  78,36,"Moputso ho tsoa ho Mong`a hau, mpho e lekaneng, –"
  78,37,"Eena Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e, le tsohle tse lipakeng, Ea Tletseng Lereko: ha ho ope ea matla ho phehisana le Eena"
  78,38,"Letsatsi leo Khabariele le manyeloi a mang ba tlang ho ema ka mahlofo, ho se ea buang kantle ho thato ea Allah, ea tletseng lereko U tla bua se nepahetseng"
  78,39,"Letsatsing leo ‘nete e tla ba pepeneneng: kahoo, ea ratang, molese a retelehele ho Mong`a hae"
  78,40,"Ruri, Re le lemositse ka kotlo e haufinyane, letsatsi leo ka lona motho a tlang ho bona seo matsoho a hae a se rometseng nale; mohana-tumelo o tla re, “Sekhobo se be honna! Hoja ke ne ke lerole!” Ka lebitso la Allah, Ea Lereko, Mong`a hao"
  79,1,Ka manyeloi a qotsulang ka soto
  79,2,Le manyeloi a qotsulang ka makhethe
  79,3,Le manyeloi a potlakelang ho ea thomong
  79,4,Joale ha e ka a peisong
  79,5,A laolang liketsahalo
  79,6,Mohla letsatsi leo Terompeta e letsoang lekhetlo la pele
  79,7,E latela ka phethako
  79,8,Lipelo li tla be li khathatseile mohlang oo
  79,9,Mahlo a talimile fats`e
  79,10,"Ba re: “Eng! Re tla busetsoa maemong a rona a mathomo"
  79,11,Eng! – re ne re le masapo a bolileng?”
  79,12,"Ba re: “Ruri! Seo e tla be el e poelo ea tahlehelo.”"
  79,13,Ruri! E tla ba ka molumo o le mong feela
  79,14,Ba tla be ba tsohile
  79,15,Na pale ea Moshe ha es’o finyelle ho uena
  79,16,Bonang! Mong`a hau U kile A memetsa ho eena phuleng e halalelang ea Tuwa
  79,17,“Tsamaea o ee ho Faro –hobane Ruri! O tlotse meeli eohle –
  79,18,"U re ho eena: na u lakatsa ho hloekisoa sebeng"
  79,19,"Hore ke u tataisetse ho Mong`a hau, u tle u mo ts’abe?”"
  79,20,Eaba Moshe o mo bonts’a sesupo se seholohali
  79,21,Empa o ile a latola a nyefola
  79,22,"Ho feta mona a furalla, a tsitlallela nyefolong"
  79,23,"Eaba o khobokanya sechaba sa hae, a hooa"
  79,24,"A re: “ke Mong`a lona, ea phahameng ka ho fetisisang.”"
  79,25,Allah U ile a mo otla le hona ho mo etsa mohlala bophelong bona le ho Bo-tlang
  79,26,Ruri! Sena ke temoso ho mang le mang ea ts’abang Allah
  79,27,Eng! Na tlholeho ea lona e boima kapa tlholeho e boima ke’a leholimo? Le hlotsoeng ke Allah
  79,28,"Ebile o phahamisitse leholimo holimo-limo, a le neha taolo le phetheho"
  79,29,"Bosiu ba lona A le neha lefifi, ho bo khabisa A bo fa khanya"
  79,30,Le lefats`e A le pharalatsa
  79,31,A hlahisa metsi le makhulo holim’a lona
  79,32,Le ho tsepamisa lithaba
  79,33,Molemong oa lona le mehlape ea lona
  79,34,Kahoo mohla ho tlang sekhobo se seholohali
  79,35,Letsatsing leo motho a tlang ho hopola tsohle tseo a li sebelelitseng
  79,36,Le mollo o tla behoa pontseng ea bohle
  79,37,"Joale, ba ileng ba tlola meeli eohle"
  79,38,Ba ikhethela bophelo ba lefats’e lena
  79,39,Lehae la bona e tlabe e le Lihele
  79,40,"Hoba ileng ba bonts`a ts’abo ea ho ema kapel’a Mong`a bona mohla kahlolo, ba qobisa phefomoloho ea bona litakatsong tsa mafeela"
  79,41,Lehae la bona e tla ba Serapa (paradeisi)
  79,42,"Ba u botsa ka motsotso oo, – “Na nako ea teng e behiloeng e neng?”"
  79,43,Phatlalatso ea nako eo e o ama joang
  79,44,Ke Mong`a hau Ea tsebang motsotso le nako e behiloeng
  79,45,U mpa u le mohlokomelisi feela hoba nang le ts’abo
  79,46,"Mohlang ba tlang ho e bona, e tla ka hoja ba phetse bosiu bo le bong, kapa nako ea hoseng ho le hong"
  80,1,"A busa lifahleho, a furalla"
  80,2,Hobane ho ile ha tla monna oa sefofu ho eena
  80,3,Empa ke`ng se neng se ka u bolella hore mohlaope a ka hola
  80,4,"Kapa ho amohela temoso, le thuto ea mo atlehisa"
  80,5,Ha ele ea hopolang hore eena o ea ikhona
  80,6,Eena o mo thehela tsebe
  80,7,Le ha e le hore ha se molato oa hao ha a sa hole
  80,8,Empa haele ea tlileng ho uena ka boitelo
  80,9,Le ka ts’abo
  80,10,Ha u oa ka oa mo natsa
  80,11,Ruri sena ke temoso
  80,12,"Kahoo, lesa ea ratang ho e amohela, a e boloke khopolong"
  80,13,Kahar’a mangolo e ea hlompheha (al-lauh al-mahfuz)
  80,14,E phahame e hloekile e ea halalela
  80,15,Ka matsoho a bangoli
  80,16,"Ba hlomphehang ba hloekileng, ba toka"
  80,17,"Sekhobo se be ho motho, ke eng se entseng hore a latole Allah"
  80,18,O hlotsoe ka eng
  80,19,"Ka lerotholi la there: U mo hlotse, A mo matlafatsa ka hohle"
  80,20,Eaba U mo nolofaletsa tsela
  80,21,"A mo hlophela lefu, le ho patoa lebitleng"
  80,22,"Ka thato Ea Hae, U tla mo tsosa"
  80,23,Ha a phethisa seo Allah A mo laetseng sona
  80,24,Motho ha a ke a lemohe lijo tsa hae
  80,25,Kamoo Re nesang pula kateng
  80,26,Re petsolang lefats’e
  80,27,Re melisa lijo-thollo holim’a lona
  80,28,"Morara, le lijo tse ahang ‘mele"
  80,29,Mehloare le lipalema
  80,30,Le lirapa tse hlehleaneng ka lifate
  80,31,Le litholoana le lesere
  80,32,Ele nala molemong oa lona le mehlape
  80,33,Khabareng e tlare ho utloahala molumo o tabolang meropa ea tsebe
  80,34,Letsatsing leo motho a tla baleha ngoana’a bo
  80,35,‘Mae le ntata’e
  80,36,Mosali le bana ba hae
  80,37,"E mong le e mong letsatsing leo, o tla be a na le mats`enyeho a lekaneng ho tsotella e mong"
  80,38,"Letsatsing leo, lifahleho tse ling li tla ela"
  80,39,"Li ts’eha, li nyakalletse"
  80,40,Lifahleho tse ling tsona letsatsing leo li tla pulufala
  80,41,Li apareloe ke lefifi
  80,42,"Bao e tlabe e le balatoli ba Allah, baetsi ba tse mpe"
  81,1,Mohla letsatsi le timelang
  81,2,"Linaleli li oelang, li fifala"
  81,3,Lithaba li nyamela
  81,4,Li kamele tse ts`ehali tse emereng likhoeli li le leshome li lahluoe feela
  81,5,Liphoofolo tse hlaha li bokelloang ‘moho
  81,6,Mohla maoatle a belang
  81,7,Mephefomoloho e kopang’oang
  81,8,"Mohla lesea la ngoanana le tsetetsoeng le phela, le hlongoang lipotso –"
  81,9,Na u bolaetsoe sebe sefe
  81,10,Maqephe a manolloang
  81,11,Leholimo le arohang ka lehare
  81,12,Khanare ea mollo e qhomeletsoa
  81,13,Serapa se atametsoang haufinyane
  81,14,Phefomoloho ka ng`oe e tla tseba seo e se sebelelitseng
  81,15,Ruri ke bitsa ho linaleli ho paka
  81,16,"Topa, kapa ipate"
  81,17,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  81,18,Le ka meso ha e tebela lefifi
  81,19,Ruri! Lena ke lentsoe la morumuoa ea hlomphehang
  81,20,"Ea sitsitsoeng ka matla, le maemo kapel’a Mong`a Terone"
  81,21,"Ea hlonephehang, ea ts’epahalang"
  81,22,Molekane oa lona ha se lehlanya
  81,23,Ka ntle ho qeaqeo u ile a `monela sebakana
  81,24,Ha a pate tsebo ea tse sa bonoeng (li-jinn) ka soele
  81,25,Lena ha se lentsoe la Satane ea rohakehileng
  81,26,"Joale, le ea kae"
  81,27,Ruri ona ke molaetsa ho mafats`e ohle
  81,28,Molemong oa e mong le e mong oa lona ea ratang ho tsamaea ka nepo
  81,29,"Empa ha ho kamoo le ka ratang kantle ho thato ea Allah, – Allah `Maballi oa mafats`e. Ka lebitso la alla, Ea Lereko, Mong`a hao"
  82,1,Mohla leholimo le petsohang ka lehare
  82,2,Linaleli li hasanang
  82,3,Maoatle a tlolang meeli
  82,4,Mabitla a nyebekoloha
  82,5,Phefomoloho ka ng`oe e tla tseba seo e se rometseng nale le seo e se patileng
  82,6,Oho motho! Ke eng se o hohetseng ho tloha ho Mong`a hau Ea nala e Khaphatsehang
  82,7,"Ea U hlolileng, a U neha sebopeo A o fa lineo ka tekanyo"
  82,8,"Ka tsela e mokhahlang, A u bopa"
  82,9,Empa o latola tokelo le kahlolo
  82,10,Ruri! Ho tengba lebeli holim’a lona
  82,11,"Ba mosa ba hlomphehang,-ba ngolang"
  82,12,Ba tseba tsohle tseo le li etsang
  82,13,"Haele bohle ba lokileng, ba tla ba nyakallong"
  82,14,"Baetsalibe, – Ba tla ba kahar’a Mollo"
  82,15,Oo ba tla kena mohla Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  82,16,Ba ke ke ba o qoba
  82,17,Ke`ng se tla u hlalosetsa hore na Letsatsi la Kahlolo ke eng
  82,18,"Hape, ke`ng se tla u hlalosetsa hore na Letsatsi la Kahlolo ke eng"
  82,19,Ke letsatsi leo ka lona ho seng phefomoloho e tlang hoba le matla a ho thusa e ng`oe. Taelo letsatsing leo ke ea Allah
  83,1,Sekhobo se be holim’a baqhekanyetsi
  83,2,"Bao e reng ha ba amohela tekanyo ho batho, ba e batla e felletse"
  83,3,Empa ha ba lokela ho bekha ka tekanyo kapa ho bekhela batho; ba fana ka boima bo tlase
  83,4,Ha ba nahane hore ba tla biletsoa boikarabelong
  83,5,Mohla Letsatsi la Tonanahali
  83,6,Letsatsi leo batho ba tlang ho ema kapel’a Mong`a mafats’e
  83,7,Che! Ruri tlaleho ea baetsalibe e kahar’a sijjin –
  83,8,Keng se tla o hlalosetsa hore sijjin ke eng? –
  83,9,Tlaleho e ngoliloeng
  83,10,Sekhobo letsatsi leo se be ho ba latolang
  83,11,Ba latolang Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  83,12,"Leo ho seng ea ka le latolang ntle le motloli oa molao, moetsalibe"
  83,13,"Ha a pheteloa Lits’enolo tsa Rona, a re: “Lits’omo tsa mehleng ea khale.”"
  83,14,Che! Empa lipelong tsa bona ke mabali a tseo ba li etsang
  83,15,Ruri! Letsatsing leo ba tla siroa ho bona khanya e tsoang ho Mong`a bona
  83,16,Khabareng ba tla kena mollong oa Lihele
  83,17,"Ho tla thoe ho bona: “Sena ke nnete eo le e latotseng le re ke leshano!”"
  83,18,Ruri tlaleho ea ba lokileng e bolokiloe ‘iliyin –
  83,19,Keng se tla le hlalosetsa hore ‘iliyin ke eng
  83,20,Tlaleho e ngoliloeng
  83,21,E pakelang ba haufinyane le Allah
  83,22,Ruri ba lokileng ba tla ba nyakallong (paradeising)
  83,23,"Literoneng, ba tla talima lintho tsohle"
  83,24,U tla ba tseba ka khanya e phatsimang lifahlehong
  83,25,"Lenyora la bona le tla kholisoa ka seno sa morara, o bitieletsoeng"
  83,26,"Sekoahelo sa teng e tla ba “musk”: molemong oa sena ba lakatsang tlhonolofatso ha ba hahabelle teng"
  83,27,Ba tla e fuoa le motsoako oa tasnim
  83,28,Seliba seo ho noang ba atametseng haufi le Allah
  83,29,Baetsalibe ba ne ba tloaetse ho soma ba-kholoang
  83,30,Ha ba ne ba feta pela bona ba ne ba panyetsana
  83,31,"Nakong eo ba boelang ho mehahabo bona, ba khutla ba soma"
  83,32,"Ha ba ba bona, ebe ba re: “Bonang bana ke ba khelohileng Ruri.”"
  83,33,Empa ha ba ea romelloa ho ba balebeli ba bona
  83,34,Letsatsi leo ba-kholoang ba tla ts’eha mahana-tumelo
  83,35,"Literoneng, ba tla talima lintho tsohle"
  83,36,Na mahana-tumelo a ke keng a lefshoa ho latela liketso tseo a neng a li etsa
  84,1,Mohla leholimo le qhashohang ka lehare
  84,2,Le thea-tsebe ho Mong`a lona. Le tlamehile
  84,3,Ha lefats’e le batalatsoa
  84,4,"Le hlohlolla se ka hara lona, le sala le hlobotse"
  84,5,"Le thea-tsebe ho Mong`a lona, le tlamehile"
  84,6,"Oho motho! Ruri o khasetsa ho Mong`a hau, u khasa ka thata, – empa u tla kopana le Eena"
  84,7,Haele ea tla fuoa tlaleho ea hae ka letsohong la molema
  84,8,U tla be a tlaleha bobe
  84,9,"U tla retellehela ho ba habo, a thabile"
  84,10,Empa ea fuoang tlaleho ea hae ka morao
  84,11,O tla llela timelo
  84,12,O tla kena lelakabeng la mollo
  84,13,"Ruri! O phetse le beng ka eena, ka nyakallo"
  84,14,Ruri! O ne a nahana hore ha a na khutlela ho Rona
  84,15,"Che, che! Mong`a hae haesale a mo shalimme"
  84,16,Kahoo ke hlapanya ka mahlaseli a letsatsi ha le hlahlamela litaba
  84,17,Bosiu le tseo bo-ikapesitseng ka tsona
  84,18,"Le ka ngoeli, e tolokile"
  84,19,Le tla tsamaea sebaka le sebaka
  84,20,Molato ke’ng ka bona haele moo ba hloka tumelo
  84,21,"Ha ba balloa Qur`an, ba sa khumamele Allah"
  84,22,Empa mahana-tumelo a latola
  84,23,Empa Allah u na le tsebo e phahametseng ka tseoba li patang
  84,24,Kahoo u ba tsebise ka kotlo e bohloko
  84,25,"Kantle ho ba-kholoang, ba liketso tse lokileng; moputso oa bona oo ke keng oa thisa"
  85,1,Ka leholimo le linaleli tse jeroeng ke lona
  85,2,Ka le Letsatsi le Ts’episitsoeng
  85,3,"Ka ea pakang, le se pakoang"
  85,4,Ho malimabe baepi ba mokoti
  85,5,Mollo o beseletsoang
  85,6,Bona! ba ne ba tjamme pel’a ona
  85,7,Ke lipaki ho tseo ba neng ba li etsa khahlanong le ba-kholoang
  85,8,"Ba ba hlokofalitse kantle ho lebaka haese feela hore ba kholoa ho Allah, Ea Matla Oohle, U ts’oanetsoe ke Lithoriso tsohle"
  85,9,Eo `Muso oa maholimo e leng oa Hae le lefats`e! Allah ke Paki ea lintho tsohle
  85,10,"Haele ba hobosang ba-kholoang, banna le basali, ba sa retellehele ka boinyatso(ho Allah), ba tla fumana kahlolo ea Lihele: ba tla otloa ka mollo o tukang"
  85,11,"Ho ba-kholoang, ba etsang ketso tse lokileng, e tlaba lirapa tseo linoka li phallang tlasa tsona. Seo ke pholoho e babatsehang"
  85,12,Ruri letsoho la Mong`a hau le matla
  85,13,"Ke Eena Ea hlolang ho tloha mathomong, A boele A phete"
  85,14,"U ts’oarela ka mehla, U Tletse Lerato-le-Mohau"
  85,15,Mong`a Terone e Tlotlehang
  85,16,Moetsi oa tsohle tseo A li rerang
  85,17,Na pale ea mabotho e fihlile ho uena
  85,18,A Faro le a Ba – Thamud
  85,19,Empa mahana-tumelo a lula a latola
  85,20,Empa Allah U ba kopetse ka morao
  85,21,Che! Sena ke Qur`an e tlotlehang
  85,22,E ngoliloeng letlapeng e babaletsoeng
  86,1,Ka leholimo le moeti oa bosiu
  86,2,Keng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na moeti oa bosiu keng
  86,3,"Ke Naleli, e khanyang"
  86,4,Ha ho phefomoloho e hlokang molebeli
  86,5,Motho ha a nahane seo a hlotsoeng ka sona
  86,6,O hlotsoe ka lerotholi la there –
  86,7,Le kollang lipakeng tsa mahalapa le likhopo
  86,8,Ruri Allah U na le matla a ho mo phelisa
  86,9,Letsatsi leo liphiri li tlang ho utolloa
  86,10,Motho ha a na ba le matla kapa mothusi
  86,11,Ka leholimo le fanang ka pula
  86,12,Le ka lefats’e le petsohang
  86,13,Ruri! Lena ke lentsoe le arolang botle le bobe
  86,14,Ha se ntho ea papali
  86,15,"Haele bona, ba etsa morero"
  86,16,Le ‘Na ke loha leano
  86,17,Kahoo fana ka nyehlisetso ho mahana-tumelo; u ba fe phomolo ha nakoana
  87,1,"Tlotlisa lebitso la Mohlokomeli-Mong`a hau, Ea Okametseng Tsohle"
  87,2,"Ea hlotseng, Ea faneng ka taelo"
  87,3,"Ea hlomathitseng melao, Ea fanang ka tataiso"
  87,4,Ea hlahisang lekhulo
  87,5,Hamorao le fetohe lehlare
  87,6,"Ka mekhahlelo Re u ruta ho bala, hore u se ke oa lebala"
  87,7,"Kantle ho thato ea Allah, hoba U tseba tse pepeneneng le tse sephiring"
  87,8,Re tla nolofatsa tsela e u lebisang tseleng e otlolohileng
  87,9,"Ka hona fana ka keletso, ha keletso e le molemo"
  87,10,Keletso e tla amoheloa ke ba nang le ts’abo
  87,11,Empa e tla qobjoa ke ba malimabe
  87,12,Ba tlang ho kena Khanareng ea Mollo
  87,13,Oo kahara ona ba sa tlong ho shoa kapa ho phela
  87,14,Ba tla atleha ke ba itlhoekisang
  87,15,"Ba rorisa lebitso la Mohlokomeli-Mong`a bona, ka thapelo"
  87,16,"Che, le khetha bophelo ba lefats’e lena"
  87,17,"Empa bophelo Bo-tlang bo molemo, ha bo fele"
  87,18,"Ka sena se har’a mangolo a mathomo, –"
  87,19,Mangolo a Abrahama le Moshe
  88,1,Na nalane ea timelo e ile ea u fihlela
  88,2,Lifahleho tse ling li tla phoqeha mohla tsatsi leo
  88,3,"Li be mats’oenyehong, li tepelle, –"
  88,4,Li kene lelakabeng la Mollo
  88,5,"Khabareng ba fuoe metsi, a belang ho noa, ho tsoa Selibeng se belang"
  88,6,"Ha ba na ho fumana lijo, haese litholoana tse babang"
  88,7,"Tse sa tlong ho aha ‘mele, kapa ho khorisa"
  88,8,Lifahleho tse ling li tla nyakalla mohla oo
  88,9,Ke thabo ho latela ts’ebetso ea bona
  88,10,Serapeng se phahameng
  88,11,Moo ba ke keng ba utloa lipuo tse hlohlonts’ang litsebe
  88,12,Moo Seliba se kopotsang
  88,13,Moo Li-Terone tse phahameng li leng teng
  88,14,Mepotjoana e behiloeng
  88,15,Mesangoana e behiloeng ka mekhahlelo
  88,16,Le meseme e nonofetseng
  88,17,Ha ba bone kamoo likamele li hlotsoeng
  88,18,Kamoo leholimo le phahamisitsoeng
  88,19,Le kamoo lithaba li tsepamisitsoeng
  88,20,Le kamoo lefats’e le aliloeng
  88,21,"Kahoo ba hlomekomelise, hobane u mohlokomelisi"
  88,22,Ha u molebeli oa litaba tsa bona
  88,23,"Empa ha mong a furalla, a latola Allah"
  88,24,Allah u tla mo ahlola ka kotlo e boima
  88,25,Poelo ea bona e ho Rona
  88,26,"Ho ho Rona, ho ba biletsa maikarabellong"
  89,1,Ka meso
  89,2,Le ka masiu a leshome
  89,3,Le ka libopuoa tsohle tsa Allah
  89,4,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  89,5,Holim’a lits’upiso tsena ho teng bopaki ho ba utloisisang
  89,6,Na ha u elelloe kamoo Mong`a hau A ileng A sebetsa kateng ka morabe oa Ba-Ad
  89,7,"Ba motse oa Iram, ka lits’ia tse phahameng"
  89,8,Bao ho es’ong ho be le tlholeho e ts’oanang le’a bona lefats’eng
  89,9,Joaloka morabe oa Ba – Thamude o ileng oa betla majoe kahar’a phula
  89,10,"Le Faro, Morena oa Lipalo"
  89,11,Bao kaofela ha bona ebileng batloli ba meeli eohle holim’a lefats’e
  89,12,Le hona ho fehla lehloeo kahar’a tsona
  89,13,Mong`a hau U ile A ts’ollela sekhobo sa kahlolo ea Hae holim’a bona
  89,14,Ruri! Ha ho se patehileng ho Mong`a hau
  89,15,"Joaloka motho eo ereng ha Mong`a hae A mo leka ka ho mo neha hlompho, A bile A ba lereko malebana le eena, e be o re: “Mong`a ka U mphile hlompho.”"
  89,16,"Empa hang ha A mo neha teko ka ho khutsufatsa mekhoa ea bophelo ba hae, o re: “Mong`a ka U ntlontlolotse.”"
  89,17,Che! Empa lona le hloloa ho hauhela khutsana
  89,18,Ha le khothaletsane phepo ea mafutsana
  89,19,Le ja mafa lekemekeme ka bonyollo bohle
  89,20,Le bile le rata leruo ka lerato le hlollang
  89,21,Che! mohla lefats’e le fetohang lehlohlojane le thumisehileng
  89,22,Mong`a hau A theoha le manyeloi a entse mekhahlelo ka mekhahlelo
  89,23,"Le lihele li atametsoa haufinyane; Ruri! Ke mohla motho a tlang ho hopola, empa mohopolo oo o tla mo thusa kang"
  89,24,"Motho o tla re: “Ao! Hoja ke mpile ka etsa letsete molemong oa bophelo ba ka!”"
  89,25,Ruri! O tla ahloloa ka kahlolo es’o kang e bonoa mohla letsatsi leo
  89,26,Ebile ha ho ea tlamang kamoo A tlamang kateng
  89,27,"Ho tla thoe hoba lokileng: “Oho lona! Meea ea lona ha e ke e phomole ka khotso"
  89,28,Khutlelang ho Mong`a lona le khotsofetse monyakeng o molemo oa Hae
  89,29,Kenang kahar’a makhabunyane a Ka
  89,30,Kahar’a serapa sa Ka!”
  90,1,Ke hlapanya ka motse-moholo ona (Makka) –
  90,2,Le uena u molokolohi oa motse-moholo ona –
  90,3,U motsoali le ngoana
  90,4,Ruri! Re hlotse motho hore a sebetse a fufuleloe
  90,5,Ha a nahane hore ha ho ope ea nang le matla holima hae
  90,6,"Mohlomong a ka re: “Ke harintse leruo le leholohali!”"
  90,7,Ha a nahane hore ha ho ope ea ‘monang
  90,8,Na ha se Rona ba mo sitsitseng ka mahlo a mabeli
  90,9,Le leleme le lipounama tse peli
  90,10,Le ho `montsa litsela tse peli
  90,11,Empa ha a potlakela tseleng e moepa –
  90,12,Ke`ng se tla le hlakisetsa na tsela e moepa ke`ng? –
  90,13,Ho neha lekhabunyane bolokolohi
  90,14,Kapa ho fana ka lijo matsatsing a tlala
  90,15,Ho khutsana ea leloko la hau
  90,16,Kapa ho mofutsana ea tlaleng ea boja-likata
  90,17,"Ka hona a tlaba har’a ba-kholoang, a khothaletsa ho ba le mamello le ho khothaletsa ho ba mosa le kutloelo bohloko"
  90,18,Bao ke balekane ba tla ba letsohong la molema
  90,19,"Empa haele ba latolang Lits’upo tsa Rona, ke balekane ba letsoho la ntsohohlo"
  90,20,Mollo e tla ba sekhele sa bona
  91,1,Ka letsatsi le khanya ea lona
  91,2,Ka ngoeli e le latelang
  91,3,Ka lets`eare ha le bontsa mahlaseli
  91,4,Ka bosiu ha bo le koahela
  91,5,Ka motheo oa leholimo le sebopeho sa lona
  91,6,Ka lefats’e le bophar`a ba lona
  91,7,Ka phefumoloho le tekanyetso le taelo eo e filoeng
  91,8,Le tataiso khethollong ho se setle le se sebe
  91,9,Ruri! Ea atlehang ke ea itlhoekisang
  91,10,Ea sa atleheng ke ea its’ilafatsang
  91,11,Ba-Thamude ba ile ba koeneha ka mekhoa ea bona e nyonts`ang
  91,12,"Bonang, monna oa moetsalibe ka ho fitisisa har’a bona o ile a khethoa"
  91,13,"Eaba moromuoa oa Allah o re ho bona: “Ke kamele ea Allah, kahoo e leseng e noe!”"
  91,14,"Empa ba ile ba mo nyelisa ba e bolaea, eaba Allah U oa ba ripitla ho latela sebe sa bona le hona ho siea malapa a bona ele masupi"
  91,15,Ha A na ts’abo ea litlamorao tsa teng
  92,1,Ha ho shoalana
  92,2,Le ha letsatsi le chaba
  92,3,Le ka Ea hlotseng monna le mosali
  92,4,Ruri! Liketso tsa hau li fapane
  92,5,Haele ea fanang le ho ts`aba Allah
  92,6,Le ho lumela ho se lokileng
  92,7,Re tla ba nolofaletsa tsela e lebisang boemong bo nepahetseng
  92,8,Empa ea khoaelang le ho inahana e le maikhona
  92,9,A latola se lokileng
  92,10,Re tla nolofatsa tsela e mo lebisang bothateng
  92,11,A maruo a hae a ka mo pholosa nakong eo a timelang
  92,12,Ruri! Ts’ebetso ea Rona ke ho fana ka tataiso
  92,13,Hobane Ruri! Qalo le qetello kea Rona
  92,14,Ke le lemositse ka lelakabe la mollo
  92,15,Ha ho ea tla cha teng ntle feela le ea qoetseng sebeng
  92,16,Ba latotseng le hona ho kheloha
  92,17,Haele ba lokileng ba tla o qoba
  92,18,Ba fanang ka leruo la bona hore ba tle ba hloeke moeeng
  92,19,Likelellong ba sa lebella molemo oa moputso ho tla ho bona
  92,20,Empa e le hona ho tsomana le sefahleho sa Mong`a bona Ea Phahameng ka ho fetisisa
  92,21,Haufinyana ba tla fumana khotsofalo
  93,1,Ka khalalelo ea khanya ea mats`a
  93,2,Le ka bosiu nakong eo bo es’ong ho se ts’ekhe
  93,3,Hore Mong`a hau ha A es’o u lahle kherehloa le hona ho u hloea
  93,4,Bophelo Bo-tlang bo tla ba molemo ho uena ho feta ba lefats’e
  93,5,Mong`a hau U tla u neha tsohle tse molemo hore u tle u khotsofale
  93,6,"Na ha se eena ea u fumaneng u le khutsana, a u lopolla"
  93,7,"Na ha se Eena Ea u fumaneng u ntse u phaqola, A u tataisa"
  93,8,"Na ha se Eena Ea u fumaneng u hloka letho, A u ruisa"
  93,9,"Ka lebaka leo, u se hatelle khutsana"
  93,10,Le hona ho leleka mokopi
  93,11,U phatlalatse nala ea Mong`a hau
  94,1,Na ha se Rona ba atollotseng sefuba sa hau
  94,2,Ra u imulla moroalo
  94,3,O neng o u roba mokokotlo
  94,4,Le hona ho tumisa boemo ba hau
  94,5,Ruri! Ho teng topollo mathateng ohle
  94,6,Ruri! Mathateng oohle ho teng topollo
  94,7,"Kahoo, ha u lopolotsoe, tsitlellela ho sebetsa ka thata"
  94,8,U retellehele ho Mong`a hau
  95,1,Ka Feikha le Olive
  95,2,Le ka Thaba ea Sinai
  95,3,Le ka motse o ts’ireletsong
  95,4,Ruri! Re hlotse motho ka tlholeho e babatsehang
  95,5,Eaba Re mo kokobetsa ka boemo bo tlase-tlase
  95,6,"Ntle le feela ea kholoang a etsa liketso tse lokileng, bao moputso oa bona o ke ke oa sitoa"
  95,7,Ke eng joale se ka o emang pele malebana le kahlolo
  95,8,Na ha se Allah Moahloli Ea Seli
  96,1,Bala! Ka lebitso la Mong`a hau Ea hlotseng
  96,2,Ea hlotseng motho ka lehloele la mali
  96,3,Bala! Mong`a hau U lereko le fetisisang
  96,4,Ea rutang ho ngola ka pene
  96,5,O rutile motho seo a sa se tsebeng
  96,6,Che! Empa motho o tlola meeli
  96,7,Ka ho nahana hore ke maikhona
  96,8,Ruri! Poelo ea tsohle e ho Mong`a hau
  96,9,Na o kile oa bona ea sitisang
  96,10,Lekhabunyane nakong eo le rapelang
  96,11,Na u kile oa bona ebang o its’etlehile tataisong
  96,12,Kapa o khothaletsa hoba mosa
  96,13,"Na o kile oa bona ebang u latola tataiso `nete, o oa furalla"
  96,14,Na ha a elelloe hore Allah U’a bona
  96,15,"Ha a hlokomele! ha a sa khaotse, re tla mo tutla ka qoba ea moriri –"
  96,16,"O leshano, o bile o silafetse –"
  96,17,"Joale, ha a bitse bathusi ba hae"
  96,18,Re tla bitsa manyeloi a kahlolo
  96,19,Se ka mo natsa. Empa u ithapalatse le hona ho ba haufinyane le Allah
  97,1,Ruri! Qura’n Re e senotse ka bosiu ba matla
  97,2,Ke eng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na bosiu ba matla ke eng
  97,3,Bosiu ba matla bo molemo ho feta likhoeli tse sekete
  97,4,Ke nako eo manyeloi le Khabariele ba theohelang lefats’eng ka tumello ea Mong`a bona le ka melao eohle
  97,5,Khotso!... Sena Ho fihlela chabo ea letsatsi
  98,1,"Haele ba latolang har’a Batho ba Lengolo le har`a ba hedene, ba ne ba ke ke ba sokoloha ho fihlela sesupo se hlakileng se finyeletse ho bona"
  98,2,"Sa moromuoa ea tsoang ho Allah, ea balang maqephe a hloekileng"
  98,3,"A jereng melao e nepahetseng, e topileng"
  98,4,Batho ba Lengolo ba ne ba ke ke ba arohana ho fihlela kamor’a hoba sesupo se hlakileng se finyelle ho bona
  98,5,"Ba ne ba laetsoe ho sebeletsa Allah le ho boloka tumelo ea bona e hloekile malebana le Eena, e be batho ba topileng ka tlholeho le hona ho phethahatsa lithapelo le ho fana ka linyehelo. Seo ke tumelo ea ‘nete"
  98,6,"Haele ba latolang har’a batho ba Lengolo le har`a bahedene, ba tla eba mollong-oa-lihele ho phela teng. Ke libopuoa tse nyonts’ang"
  98,7,"Bohle ba-kholoang, ba etsa liketso tse lokileng, – bona ke libopuoa tse molemo"
  98,8,"Moputso oa bona o ho Allah: lirapa tsa Edene, tseo linoka li phallang tlas’a tsona, ba tla phela teng kahosafeleng. Allah U tla nyakalla ke bona le bona ba tla nyakalla ke Eena. Tsena li molemong oa ba ts’abang Mong`a bona"
  99,1,Ha lefats’e le sisingoa la mathetho
  99,2,Le itlhohlolla moroalo
  99,3,"Motho o tla re: “Molato ke eng ka lefats’e”"
  99,4,Ke mohla lefat’se le tla bolela nalane ea lona
  99,5,Hobane Mong`a hau U tla le susumetsa
  99,6,Mohlang oo batho ba tla nyolosa ba theosa ka mekhahlelo ho ea bonts’oa liketso tsa bona
  99,7,Mong le mong ea etsang ketso e lokileng e fokolang sa ntoana- la-botsikoane o tla e bona
  99,8,Mong le mong ea etsang sebe le ha se ka fokola sa ntoana-la- botsikoane o tla se bona
  100,1,"Ka lipitsi tse mathang, tse hemeselang"
  100,2,Tseo maotong a tsona ho qobang litlhase
  100,3,Tse tsometsang tlhaselo ka matjeke
  100,4,E be li tsosa leroele khabong
  100,5,Li parola lebotho la lira ka lehare e le ngatana ng’oe
  100,6,Ruri! Motho o hloka teboho ho Mong`a hae
  100,7,E bile ke paki holim’a seo
  100,8,O lehala leratong la leruo
  100,9,Na ha a tsebe hore mohla mabitla a hlatsang likateng
  100,10,Se ka lifubeng tsa batho se tla behoa pepeneneng
  100,11,Letsatsing leo Mong`a bona U tlabe A tseba tsohle tsa bona
  101,1,Sekhobo
  101,2,Sekhobo ke eng
  101,3,Ebe ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore na sekhobo ke eng
  101,4,Ke letsatsi leo batho ba tla hasana joaloka lirurubele
  101,5,Lithaba li tla ba joalo ka boea
  101,6,Bao liketso tsa bona li tla imela sekala
  101,7,Ba tla phela bophelo ba nyakallo
  101,8,Empa eo liketso tsa hae li tla fokola sekaleng
  101,9,Lehae la hae e tla ba Lihele
  101,10,E be ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore na lihele ke eng
  101,11,Ke mollo o hlenneng
  102,1,Phehisano ea pokello ea matlotlo e le khelositse
  102,2,Ho fihlela le etela mabitleng
  102,3,Che! Haufinyane le tla tseba
  102,4,Hape le tla tseba
  102,5,Che! Hoja le na le tsebo e tehileng
  102,6,Hobane le tla bona mollo oa Lihele
  102,7,Hape le tla o bona ka tiieo
  102,8,Letsatsing leo le tla botsoa khahlano le monyaka oa lefats’e lena
  103,1,Ka Nako
  103,2,Ruri! Motho o tahlehong
  103,3,"Kantle ho ba-kholoang, ba etsang liketso tse lokileng, ba khothalletsang ‘nete le ba nang le mamello"
  104,1,Sekhobo se be ho moqabanyi e mong le e mong le raleshano
  104,2,Ea khobokantseng leruo la lefats’e lena le ho le bala
  104,3,O nahana hore leruo la hae le tla etsa hore a phele kahosafeleng
  104,4,Che! Ruri! O tla tjebeloa mollong o harinyang
  104,5,E be ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore mollo o harinyang
  104,6,Ke mollo oa Allah U hotelitsoeng
  104,7,Oo qhomelang holim’a lipelo tsa batho
  104,8,Ruri! o tlaba kupetsa
  104,9,Kahar’a lits’iea tse otlolotsoeng
  105,1,Na ha u ea bona kamoo Mong`a hau A ileng A ripitla balekane ba tlou kateng
  105,2,Ha A ka A nyopisa morero oa bona
  105,3,A romella mohlape oa linonyana khahlano le bona
  105,4,Ho ba furuletsa ka majoe a lenyetana
  105,5,A ba fetola lehlare
  106,1,Ka selekane sa Ma-Qureysh
  106,2,Re ile Ra etsa hore ba simolle maeto mariha le lehlabula
  106,3,Ha ba khumamele Mong`a ntlo ena
  106,4,Ea ba fepang khahlanong le tlala le ho ba sireletsa matsoalong a bona
  107,1,U kile oa bona motho ea latolang kahlolo
  107,2,Ke ea lelekang khutsana
  107,3,Ea sa khothaletseng ho feptjoa ha mafutsana
  107,4,Aa! Sekhobo se be holim’a barapeli
  107,5,Ba sa tsotelleng thapelo ea bona
  107,6,Ba etsetsang ho bonoa
  107,7,Ba hana ka litokelo tsa boahisane
  108,1,Ruri Re u nehile tlotla ea Seliba Paradeising
  108,2,"Kahoo, retelehela ho Mong`a hau ka thapelo, u etse sehlabelo"
  108,3,Ruri! Ke sera sa hau se tlang ho hloka bokamoso
  109,1,"E re: “Oho lona mahana-tumelo"
  109,2,Ha ke khumamele seo le se khumamelang
  109,3,Le lona ha le khumamele seo ke se khumamelang
  109,4,Ha nkeke ka khumamela seo le se khumamelang
  109,5,Etsoe le ke keng la khumamela seo ke se khumamelang
  109,6,"Tumelo ea lona ke ea lona, ea ka ke ea ka"
  110,1,Ha thuso le tlholo ea Allah li fihlang
  110,2,U bona lichaba li inehela tumelong ea Allah ka mekhopi
  110,3,"Keteka lithoriso tsa Mong`a hau, kopa ts’oarelo ho Eena: ke Eena Ea amohelang boinyatso, Ea Ts`oarelang"
  111,1,Ha mats`oho a Lahab a timele! Ha a timele
  111,2,Ha ho moputso maruong a hae le ho tseo a li bokellelitseng
  111,3,Haufi o tlaba mollong o khanare ea lelakabe
  111,4,Mohatsa`e o tla roala patsi e le libeso
  111,5,Thapo e lohiloeng ka makhapetla a palema e haretsoe molaleng oa hae (mohatsae)
  112,1,"E re: Ke Allah, Ea Inotsi"
  112,2,"Allah, Rabosafeleng"
  112,3,"Ha A tsoale, ha A tsoaloa"
  112,4,Ha ho ea ts’oanang le Eena
  113,1,"E re: Ke kopa ts’ireletso ho Mong`a meso"
  113,2,Khahlanong le tse silafetseng tse hlotsoeng
  113,3,Ka ho ts’oana le tse silafetseng tsa lefifing le noelletseng
  113,4,Le khahlanong le bobe ba balohi ba mafito
  113,5,Le khahlanong le bobe ba bahonuhi ha ba honoha
  114,1,"E re: ke kopa ts’ireletso ho Mong`a batho bohle"
  114,2,Morena oa batho
  114,3,Mopi oa batho
  114,4,"Khahlanong le linyonts`a tsa mosebi ea soto, ea hoeshetsang a be a nyamele"
  114,5,Ea silafatsang lipelo tsa batho
  114,6,Har’a masabonoeng (li-jinn) le har`a batho